Dialogue: 0.0:00:03.63.0:00:05.31.Default..0.0.0..BREAKS MY HEART.
Dialogue: 0.0:00:05.33.0:00:07.11.Default..0.0.0..MY HEART'S BROKEN RIGHT NOW.
Dialogue: 0.0:00:10.34.0:00:13.49.Default..0.0.0..MY GIRLFRIEND WAS DANCING LIKE\NA FUCKIN' PIG IN FRONT OF ME.
Dialogue: 0.0:00:13.51.0:00:14.95.Default..0.0.0..WHAT DO YOU WANT ME TO DO?\NA PIG?
Dialogue: 0.0:00:14.98.0:00:17.12.Default..0.0.0..I NEED A BREAK FROM YOU.\NI DON'T WANT TO TALK TO YOU.
Dialogue: 0.0:00:17.15.0:00:18.39.Default..0.0.0..EXCUSE ME?\NI'M SORRY.
Dialogue: 0.0:00:18.41.0:00:21.16.Default..0.0.0..I DON'T WANT TO TALK TO YOU.
Dialogue: 0.0:00:21.18.0:00:22.46.Default..0.0.0..I WOULD TAKE CARE OF YOU
Dialogue: 0.0:00:22.48.0:00:24.30.Default..0.0.0..LIKE YOU'VE NEVER BEEN\NTAKEN CARE OF BEFORE.
Dialogue: 0.0:00:24.32.0:00:27.63.Default..0.0.0..I LOVE YOU.\NI DO.
Dialogue: 0.0:00:27.66.0:00:30.10.Default..0.0.0..I'M LAYING IN BED.\NSNOOKI COMES IN.
Dialogue: 0.0:00:30.13.0:00:31.20.Default..0.0.0..SO WHAT AM I GONNA DO?
Dialogue: 0.0:00:31.23.0:00:32.54.Default..0.0.0..FUCKIN' THROW HER OUT\NOF THE ROOM?
Dialogue: 0.0:00:32.56.0:00:33.77.Default..0.0.0..NO.
Dialogue: 0.0:00:33.80.0:00:35.61.Default..0.0.0..I SEE THE BLANKET\NMOVING UP AND DOWN.
Dialogue: 0.0:00:35.63.0:00:37.18.Default..0.0.0..SNOOKI'S HEAD POPPING UP\NFOR AIR.
Dialogue: 0.0:00:37.20.0:00:38.91.Default..0.0.0..WE ALL KNOW WHAT'S GOING DOWN.
Dialogue: 0.0:00:41.34.0:00:42.75.Default..0.0.0..DJ PAULY DELVECCHIO!
Dialogue: 0.0:00:42.77.0:00:45.35.Default..0.0.0..I'M GOING TO JERSEY SHORE.\NBITCH!
Dialogue: 0.0:00:45.37.0:00:47.82.Default..0.0.0..ALL RIGHT.\NWE GOT A SITUATION.
Dialogue: 0.0:00:47.84.0:00:50.05.Default..0.0.0..I'M THE SWEETEST BITCH\NYOU'LL EVER MEET.
Dialogue: 0.0:00:52.38.0:00:54.93.Default..0.0.0..AFTER I HAVE SEX WITH A GUY.\NI WILL RIP THEIR HEADS OFF.
Dialogue: 0.0:00:54.95.0:00:57.33.Default..0.0.0..GO. VINNY!\NGO. VINNY!
Dialogue: 0.0:00:57.35.0:00:59.45.Default..0.0.0..YOU LIKE THE BOOBS?
Dialogue: 0.0:01:22.11.0:01:24.32.Default..0.0.0..WHAT THE FUCK\NJUST HAPPENED?
Dialogue: 0.0:01:24.35.0:01:28.46.Default..0.0.0..WHAT DID YOU JUST DO?
Dialogue: 0.0:01:28.48.0:01:29.73.Default..0.0.0..LET'S GO DO SOMETHING.
Dialogue: 0.0:01:31.32.0:01:34.37.Default..0.0.0..YOU NEVER GET ME UP\NAT 7:00 IN THE MORNING.
Dialogue: 0.0:01:34.39.0:01:36.94.Default..0.0.0..I'M UP!\NI'M FREAKING UP.
Dialogue: 0.0:01:36.96.0:01:38.44.Default..0.0.0..AND YOU KNOW WHY I'M UP?
Dialogue: 0.0:01:38.46.0:01:43.14.Default..0.0.0..BECAUSE I FUCKING SLEPT\NIN VINNY'S BED LAST NIGHT.
Dialogue: 0.0:01:43.17.0:01:44.81.Default..0.0.0..I'M UP.
Dialogue: 0.0:01:44.83.0:01:46.68.Default..0.0.0..IF I GET A BREAKFAST PLACE.\NYOU WANT TO GO?
Dialogue: 0.0:01:46.70.0:01:48.78.Default..0.0.0..I NEED A GIRLFRIEND\NTO TALK TO RIGHT NOW.
Dialogue: 0.0:01:48.80.0:01:51.55.Default..0.0.0..IT'S 7:30 IN THE MORNING.\NBUT I SEE NICOLE.
Dialogue: 0.0:01:51.57.0:01:53.55.Default..0.0.0..LIKE. WHERE ARE YOU\NCOMING FROM. NICOLE?
Dialogue: 0.0:01:53.58.0:01:55.52.Default..0.0.0..LIKE. DID YOU PASS OUT\NIN THE LIVING ROOM?
Dialogue: 0.0:01:55.54.0:01:57.09.Default..0.0.0..DUDE. I WAITED UP ALL NIGHT\NFOR YOU.
Dialogue: 0.0:01:57.11.0:01:58.82.Default..0.0.0..WHERE WERE YOU?
Dialogue: 0.0:01:58.85.0:02:02.09.Default..0.0.0..WENT TO FUCKIN'\NVINNY'S BED.
Dialogue: 0.0:02:02.12.0:02:04.00.Default..0.0.0..JENNI. AT THIS POINT.
Dialogue: 0.0:02:04.02.0:02:05.93.Default..0.0.0..I DON'T GIVE A FUCK.
Dialogue: 0.0:02:05.96.0:02:07.80.Default..0.0.0..I DON'T CARE IF ME AND JIONNI\NARE DONE.
Dialogue: 0.0:02:07.82.0:02:09.30.Default..0.0.0..BECAUSE HE SUCKS {...}.
Dialogue: 0.0:02:09.32.0:02:11.54.Default..0.0.0..HONESTLY. I WOULD NEVER CHEAT\NON JIONNI.
Dialogue: 0.0:02:11.56.0:02:13.77.Default..0.0.0..BUT I SAID. "WE'RE DONE."\NON THE PHONE.
Dialogue: 0.0:02:13.80.0:02:15.17.Default..0.0.0..AND THAT'S WHY\NI JUST WENT CRAZY.
Dialogue: 0.0:02:15.20.0:02:18.01.Default..0.0.0..IT WAS JUST... IT WAS\NA REBOUND REACTION.
Dialogue: 0.0:02:18.03.0:02:19.78.Default..0.0.0..HOW DRUNK ARE YOU?
Dialogue: 0.0:02:19.80.0:02:21.15.Default..0.0.0..NOT THAT DRUNK.
Dialogue: 0.0:02:21.17.0:02:23.18.Default..0.0.0..'CAUSE I REALLY\NHAVE TO TALK TO YOU ANYWAYS.
Dialogue: 0.0:02:23.21.0:02:25.48.Default..0.0.0..'CAUSE I'M NEVER FUCKIN'\NTALKING TO THAT KID.
Dialogue: 0.0:02:25.51.0:02:27.19.Default..0.0.0..MIKE?\NYEAH.
Dialogue: 0.0:02:27.21.0:02:28.35.Default..0.0.0..SO WHAT WENT DOWN
Dialogue: 0.0:02:28.38.0:02:30.22.Default..0.0.0..AND HOW I DEFENDED YOU\NLAST NIGHT.
Dialogue: 0.0:02:30.25.0:02:32.52.Default..0.0.0..LAST NIGHT. MIKE TELLS US\NIN THE LIVING ROOM
Dialogue: 0.0:02:32.55.0:02:35.76.Default..0.0.0..WHEN NICOLE WASN'T AROUND\NTHAT HE GOT A {...} FROM HER.
Dialogue: 0.0:02:35.78.0:02:37.76.Default..0.0.0..I LOOKED MIKE DEAD\NIN THE FACE. AND I GO.
Dialogue: 0.0:02:37.79.0:02:39.03.Default..0.0.0.."I AM TELLING NICOLE."
Dialogue: 0.0:02:39.05.0:02:41.90.Default..0.0.0..I WAS LIKE. "SHE WILL NEVER\NCHOOSE YOU OVER JIONNI.
Dialogue: 0.0:02:41.92.0:02:43.30.Default..0.0.0..GET THAT THROUGH YOUR HEAD."
Dialogue: 0.0:02:43.32.0:02:45.37.Default..0.0.0..HE GOES. "WELL. SHE FUCKIN'\NSURE AS HELL CHOSE ME
Dialogue: 0.0:02:45.39.0:02:47.51.Default..0.0.0..OVER JIONNI WHEN SHE\NWAS {...} MY {...}."
Dialogue: 0.0:02:47.53.0:02:49.37.Default..0.0.0..CRAZY PANTS!
Dialogue: 0.0:02:49.40.0:02:51.14.Default..0.0.0..YOU'RE CRAZY PANTS!
Dialogue: 0.0:02:51.17.0:02:52.61.Default..0.0.0..I DIDN'T DO ANYTHING.
Dialogue: 0.0:02:52.64.0:02:55.45.Default..0.0.0..YEAH. I WATCHED FUCKING RYDER\NGET WITH HIS FRIEND.
Dialogue: 0.0:02:55.47.0:02:57.35.Default..0.0.0..AND THAT WAS HOT.\NWHATEVER.
Dialogue: 0.0:02:57.37.0:02:59.05.Default..0.0.0..BUT I DIDN'T FUCKING\NGET WITH MIKE.
Dialogue: 0.0:02:59.07.0:03:01.69.Default..0.0.0..AND MIKE WAS SO UPSET THAT\NI WOULDN'T HOOK UP WITH HIM.
Dialogue: 0.0:03:01.71.0:03:03.39.Default..0.0.0..'CAUSE HE'S NOT USED\NTO REJECTION.
Dialogue: 0.0:03:03.41.0:03:05.69.Default..0.0.0..I WANT TO HAIRSPRAY HIM\NIN THE FACE RIGHT NOW.
Dialogue: 0.0:03:05.71.0:03:07.33.Default..0.0.0..WHY IS THERE\NSO MUCH SCREAMING. YO?
Dialogue: 0.0:03:07.35.0:03:08.59.Default..0.0.0..WHAT THE FUCK GOING ON?
Dialogue: 0.0:03:08.62.0:03:09.79.Default..0.0.0..GET OUT OF MY ROOM.
Dialogue: 0.0:03:09.82.0:03:10.86.Default..0.0.0..-{\i1} ME{\i0} GET OUT OF YOUR ROOM?
Dialogue: 0.0:03:10.89.0:03:11.90.Default..0.0.0..YEAH.\NFOR REAL?
Dialogue: 0.0:03:11.92.0:03:13.10.Default..0.0.0..EVERYONE'S TELLING ME
Dialogue: 0.0:03:13.12.0:03:14.77.Default..0.0.0..WHAT THE FUCK YOU SAID\NABOUT ME LAST NIGHT.
Dialogue: 0.0:03:14.79.0:03:15.80.Default..0.0.0..WE'RE NOT FRIENDS.
Dialogue: 0.0:03:15.82.0:03:17.20.Default..0.0.0..MAYBE YOU SHOULD TALK\NTO ME FIRST.
Dialogue: 0.0:03:17.23.0:03:18.97.Default..0.0.0..WE'RE NOT FRIENDS.\NIT'S ALL GOOD. SNOOKS.
Dialogue: 0.0:03:18.99.0:03:20.20.Default..0.0.0..YOU'RE SO MEAN.
Dialogue: 0.0:03:20.23.0:03:21.64.Default..0.0.0..'CAUSE I'M TIRED\NOF BEING MR. NICE.
Dialogue: 0.0:03:21.66.0:03:23.31.Default..0.0.0..ALL RIGHT. TALK TO ME FIRST\NBEFORE YOU TALK
Dialogue: 0.0:03:23.33.0:03:24.51.Default..0.0.0..TO 16 OTHER PEOPLE.\NALL RIGHT?
Dialogue: 0.0:03:24.53.0:03:25.91.Default..0.0.0..I DON'T WANT TO.\NTALK TO ME FIRST!
Dialogue: 0.0:03:25.93.0:03:27.08.Default..0.0.0..I'M ALWAYS NICE.
Dialogue: 0.0:03:27.10.0:03:28.58.Default..0.0.0..DON'T FUCKING YELL\NAT ME LIKE THAT.
Dialogue: 0.0:03:28.60.0:03:29.98.Default..0.0.0..WE'RE NOT FRIENDS.\NFINE. SNOOKS.
Dialogue: 0.0:03:30.01.0:03:31.28.Default..0.0.0..WE'RE NOT FRIENDS THEN.\NSNOOKS.
Dialogue: 0.0:03:31.31.0:03:32.45.Default..0.0.0..FINE. SO GET OUT OF MY ROOM.
Dialogue: 0.0:03:32.47.0:03:33.72.Default..0.0.0..ALL DAY. BABY!\NFINE.
Dialogue: 0.0:03:33.74.0:03:35.32.Default..0.0.0..WOW.\NI MEAN. "GET THE FUCK OUT"?
Dialogue: 0.0:03:35.34.0:03:37.16.Default..0.0.0..LIKE. SHE'S LIKE\NTHE FUGITIVE RIGHT NOW.
Dialogue: 0.0:03:37.18.0:03:39.42.Default..0.0.0..AND I'M HARBORING INFORMATION.\NYOU KNOW WHAT I'M SAYING?
Dialogue: 0.0:03:39.45.0:03:40.86.Default..0.0.0..DON'T TALK SHIT\NAND YOU WON'T FEEL
Dialogue: 0.0:03:40.88.0:03:42.29.Default..0.0.0..LIKE A FUCKING DOUCHEBAG.
Dialogue: 0.0:03:42.32.0:03:43.49.Default..0.0.0..THAT'S ALL I HAVE TO SAY.
Dialogue: 0.0:03:43.52.0:03:45.03.Default..0.0.0..I JUST NEED MY BEST FRIEND.
Dialogue: 0.0:03:45.05.0:03:48.07.Default..0.0.0..SO I'M LIKE. "JENNI.\NWE'RE GOING TO GET MIMOSAS."
Dialogue: 0.0:03:48.09.0:03:50.00.Default..0.0.0..I HATE YOU.
Dialogue: 0.0:03:50.03.0:03:51.54.Default..0.0.0..ARE YOU READY. NICOLE?
Dialogue: 0.0:03:51.56.0:03:52.94.Default..0.0.0..YEAH. LET'S GO.
Dialogue: 0.0:03:52.96.0:03:55.61.Default..0.0.0..I'M SO TIRED RIGHT NOW.\NYOU CRAZY WHORE.
Dialogue: 0.0:03:55.63.0:03:57.58.Default..0.0.0..THEY BETTER HAVE MIMOSAS\NAT THIS BREAKFAST.
Dialogue: 0.0:03:57.60.0:04:00.28.Default..0.0.0..'CAUSE IF THEY DON'T.\NI'M GOING BACK TO JERSEY.
Dialogue: 0.0:04:00.30.0:04:01.51.Default..0.0.0..I HAVE TO TEACH HER\NA LESSON.
Dialogue: 0.0:04:01.54.0:04:02.81.Default..0.0.0..I HAVE TO TEACH NICOLE\NA LESSON.
Dialogue: 0.0:04:02.84.0:04:04.08.Default..0.0.0..AND THE TRUTH HAS TO COME OUT.
Dialogue: 0.0:04:04.11.0:04:06.15.Default..0.0.0..SO LET ME JUST CALL\NMY BOY UNIT
Dialogue: 0.0:04:06.17.0:04:07.82.Default..0.0.0..JUST TO REFRESH MY MEMORY
Dialogue: 0.0:04:07.84.0:04:09.25.Default..0.0.0..ON WHAT REALLY HAPPENED\NTHAT NIGHT
Dialogue: 0.0:04:09.28.0:04:10.42.Default..0.0.0..BETWEEN ME AND NICOLE.
Dialogue: 0.0:04:10.45.0:04:11.89.Default..0.0.0..MY FRIEND UNIT AND RYDER.
Dialogue: 0.0:04:11.91.0:04:13.32.Default..0.0.0..YO.\NYO. WHAT UP?
Dialogue: 0.0:04:13.35.0:04:14.89.Default..0.0.0..WHAT UP. HOMEY?
Dialogue: 0.0:04:14.92.0:04:17.40.Default..0.0.0..YO. YOU REMEMBER WHEN YOU WERE\NBANGING SNOOKI'S FRIEND RYDER?
Dialogue: 0.0:04:17.42.0:04:18.90.Default..0.0.0..RYDER. YEAH. YEAH.
Dialogue: 0.0:04:18.92.0:04:21.20.Default..0.0.0..SOMEHOW THAT STORY GOT OUT.\NYOU KNOW. THROUGHOUT THE DAY
Dialogue: 0.0:04:21.22.0:04:22.80.Default..0.0.0..AND THERE'S JUST BEEN\NMAD ARGUMENTS.
Dialogue: 0.0:04:22.83.0:04:23.94.Default..0.0.0..REALLY?
Dialogue: 0.0:04:23.96.0:04:25.17.Default..0.0.0..I KNOW YOU KNEW 100%\NABOUT IT.
Dialogue: 0.0:04:25.19.0:04:26.44.Default..0.0.0..'CAUSE YOU WERE\NBANGING RYDER.
Dialogue: 0.0:04:26.46.0:04:27.87.Default..0.0.0..AND THEN SNOOKI GOT\NA LITTLE HORNY.
Dialogue: 0.0:04:27.90.0:04:29.47.Default..0.0.0..SO SHE GOT ON HER {...}\NREAL QUICK.
Dialogue: 0.0:04:29.50.0:04:31.81.Default..0.0.0..REALLY. YOU PUT THAT-\NYOU PUT HER ON BLAST ON THAT?
Dialogue: 0.0:04:31.83.0:04:33.61.Default..0.0.0..I DID. I DEFINITELY DID\NPUT HER ON BLAST.
Dialogue: 0.0:04:33.64.0:04:35.08.Default..0.0.0..BUT YOU KNOW WHAT I MEAN.
Dialogue: 0.0:04:35.10.0:04:38.78.Default..0.0.0..SNOOKI TURNED FROM 4'9"\NTO ABOUT 2'9".
Dialogue: 0.0:04:38.81.0:04:39.98.Default..0.0.0..YOU KNOW WHAT I'M SAYING?
Dialogue: 0.0:04:40.01.0:04:41.25.Default..0.0.0..AND THEN AFTER THAT.\NSHE SAID.
Dialogue: 0.0:04:41.28.0:04:43.89.Default..0.0.0.."DON'T EVER. EVER. EVER.\NEVER SAY ANYTHING."
Dialogue: 0.0:04:43.91.0:04:46.71.Default..0.0.0..I SAID. "PINKY SWEAR."
Dialogue: 0.0:04:53.99.0:04:56.03.Default..0.0.0..THANK YOU FOR WAKING UP.
Dialogue: 0.0:04:56.06.0:04:58.37.Default..0.0.0..I LOVE YOU.\NI JUST NEED YOU IN MY LIFE.
Dialogue: 0.0:04:58.39.0:04:59.70.Default..0.0.0..THAT'S WHY\NI JUMPED OUT OF BED.
Dialogue: 0.0:04:59.73.0:05:02.07.Default..0.0.0..ESPECIALLY. LIKE. RIGHT NOW.\NYOU KNOW WHAT I MEAN?
Dialogue: 0.0:05:02.10.0:05:03.84.Default..0.0.0..WE'LL SPEND THE DAY TOGETHER\NOUTSIDE.
Dialogue: 0.0:05:03.87.0:05:06.28.Default..0.0.0..DO YOU AGREE JIONNI SUCKS?\NMM-HMM.
Dialogue: 0.0:05:06.30.0:05:07.41.Default..0.0.0..JIONNI SUCKS.
Dialogue: 0.0:05:11.34.0:05:13.58.Default..0.0.0..OH. THAT'S BOTH FOR ME.
Dialogue: 0.0:05:13.61.0:05:15.72.Default..0.0.0..OKAY.\NI'LL HAVE A SIP OF ONE.
Dialogue: 0.0:05:15.74.0:05:17.32.Default..0.0.0..NOW I'M GONNA LOOK LIKE\NTHE BAD PERSON...
Dialogue: 0.0:05:17.35.0:05:20.16.Default..0.0.0..YOU'RE NOT.\NHE PUSHED YOU SO FAR.
Dialogue: 0.0:05:20.18.0:05:21.96.Default..0.0.0..YOU'RE A GOOD GIRLFRIEND.
Dialogue: 0.0:05:21.98.0:05:23.89.Default..0.0.0..WELL. NOT ANYMORE.
Dialogue: 0.0:05:23.92.0:05:25.23.Default..0.0.0..I JUST WANTED TO CUDDLE.
Dialogue: 0.0:05:25.25.0:05:27.97.Default..0.0.0..I LOVE HIM. LIKE.\NAS A BEST FRIEND.
Dialogue: 0.0:05:27.99.0:05:30.07.Default..0.0.0..DID YOU HAVE SEX?\NNO.
Dialogue: 0.0:05:30.09.0:05:31.84.Default..0.0.0..I DON'T REMEMBER HAVING SEX.
Dialogue: 0.0:05:31.86.0:05:35.84.Default..0.0.0..I'M FIGURING. YOU KNOW.\NHE {...} ON ME.
Dialogue: 0.0:05:35.86.0:05:37.31.Default..0.0.0..I LOVE MIMOSAS.
Dialogue: 0.0:05:37.33.0:05:39.30.Default..0.0.0..I LOVE SLEEP.
Dialogue: 0.0:05:47.11.0:05:49.72.Default..0.0.0..GYM. TAN. DRAMA TODAY.
Dialogue: 0.0:05:49.74.0:05:52.59.Default..0.0.0..G.T.D.
Dialogue: 0.0:05:52.61.0:05:55.16.Default..0.0.0..SNOOKI. JIONNI.
Dialogue: 0.0:05:55.18.0:05:58.26.Default..0.0.0..GYM. TAN. WHO'S THE RAT?
Dialogue: 0.0:05:58.29.0:06:00.50.Default..0.0.0..OH. MAN. I'M JUST\NGETTING TIRED OF PEOPLE
Dialogue: 0.0:06:00.52.0:06:01.83.Default..0.0.0..JUST NOT BEING\NNICE TO ME. DOG.
Dialogue: 0.0:06:01.86.0:06:03.23.Default..0.0.0..SNOOKI. THIS MORNING.\NSHE'S LIKE.
Dialogue: 0.0:06:03.26.0:06:04.77.Default..0.0.0.."DON'T TALK TO ME AGAIN.\NFUCK YOU."
Dialogue: 0.0:06:04.79.0:06:06.24.Default..0.0.0..I WAS LIKE-\NI'M LIKE. "YO."
Dialogue: 0.0:06:06.26.0:06:08.34.Default..0.0.0..I'M LIKE. "ME AND YOU ARE CLOSE.\NLIKE. DON'T DO THIS."
Dialogue: 0.0:06:08.36.0:06:10.41.Default..0.0.0..I WANT TO SHOW PEOPLE\NIN THIS HOUSE
Dialogue: 0.0:06:10.43.0:06:12.21.Default..0.0.0..THAT YOU CAN'T BELIEVE\NEVERYTHING YOU HEAR.
Dialogue: 0.0:06:12.23.0:06:15.01.Default..0.0.0..SO I'M GOING TO TELL\NTHE ROOMMATES A LITTLE LIE.
Dialogue: 0.0:06:15.04.0:06:17.22.Default..0.0.0..AND I'M GONNA SEE\NWHO RATS THEMSELVES OUT.
Dialogue: 0.0:06:17.24.0:06:19.45.Default..0.0.0..SHE'S MAKING ME LOOK LIKE\NA LIAR. DUDE.
Dialogue: 0.0:06:19.47.0:06:20.85.Default..0.0.0..SO I'M LIKE.\N"YOU KNOW WHAT. MAN?"
Dialogue: 0.0:06:20.88.0:06:22.32.Default..0.0.0..I GAVE MY BOY UNIT\NJIONNI'S NUMBER.
Dialogue: 0.0:06:22.34.0:06:24.15.Default..0.0.0..SAID. "CALL HIM UP\NAND TELL HIM WHAT HAPPENED."
Dialogue: 0.0:06:24.18.0:06:27.06.Default..0.0.0..BUT IN REALITY.\NALL I DID IS CALL UNIT.
Dialogue: 0.0:06:27.08.0:06:29.79.Default..0.0.0..AND WE TALKED ABOUT THE STORY\NTOGETHER AND LAUGHED ABOUT IT.
Dialogue: 0.0:06:29.82.0:06:32.56.Default..0.0.0..GYM. TAN. DRAMA TODAY.
Dialogue: 0.0:06:32.59.0:06:34.33.Default..0.0.0..G.T.D.
Dialogue: 0.0:06:34.36.0:06:36.63.Default..0.0.0..SHH...
Dialogue: 0.0:06:36.66.0:06:37.87.Default..0.0.0..UH-OH.
Dialogue: 0.0:06:37.89.0:06:40.21.Default..0.0.0..SO WE'LL SEE WHAT HAPPENS NOW.
Dialogue: 0.0:06:40.23.0:06:43.41.Default..0.0.0..SAM HAD ACCIDENTALLY WALKED BY\NWHEN I HAD TOLD RON.
Dialogue: 0.0:06:43.43.0:06:46.34.Default..0.0.0..SO NOW I'VE PLANTED THE SEEDS.\NYOU KNOW?
Dialogue: 0.0:06:46.37.0:06:48.01.Default..0.0.0..IT'S GYM. TAN.\NWHO'S THE RAT?
Dialogue: 0.0:06:48.04.0:06:50.72.Default..0.0.0..DEENA.\NWHAT HAPPENED?
Dialogue: 0.0:06:50.74.0:06:52.48.Default..0.0.0..I COULD HAVE SWORN\NI JUST HEARD MIKE SAY
Dialogue: 0.0:06:52.51.0:06:54.82.Default..0.0.0..HE'S GONNA HAVE\NTHE UNIT CALL JIONNI.
Dialogue: 0.0:06:54.84.0:06:55.99.Default..0.0.0..WHY WOULD HE FUCKIN' DO THAT?
Dialogue: 0.0:06:56.01.0:06:57.39.Default..0.0.0..I DON'T KNOW\NIF I HEARD THAT RIGHT.
Dialogue: 0.0:06:57.41.0:06:59.29.Default..0.0.0..THAT'S WHY I DON'T KNOW\NIF I SHOULD SAY ANYTHING.
Dialogue: 0.0:06:59.31.0:07:01.23.Default..0.0.0..YOU KNOW. LIKE.\NIT'S NOT HIS BUSINESS
Dialogue: 0.0:07:01.25.0:07:02.69.Default..0.0.0..TO GET INVOLVED IN.
Dialogue: 0.0:07:02.72.0:07:04.10.Default..0.0.0..WHAT AN IDIOT.
Dialogue: 0.0:07:04.12.0:07:06.16.Default..0.0.0..HE COULDN'T HAVE SAID THAT.\NLIKE. THAT'S FUCKED UP.
Dialogue: 0.0:07:06.19.0:07:07.97.Default..0.0.0..I'VE BEEN UP SINCE. LIKE.\N6:30 IN THE MORNING.
Dialogue: 0.0:07:07.99.0:07:09.37.Default..0.0.0..ME TOO.
Dialogue: 0.0:07:09.39.0:07:11.54.Default..0.0.0..I WOKE UP TO PEOPLE TALKING\NSHIT6 ABOUT ME THIS MORNING.
Dialogue: 0.0:07:11.56.0:07:13.77.Default..0.0.0..JENNI AND SNOOKS.\NTHAT'S NOT COOL.
Dialogue: 0.0:07:13.80.0:07:16.41.Default..0.0.0..SO JUST TO EVEN UP THE ODDS.
Dialogue: 0.0:07:16.43.0:07:18.84.Default..0.0.0..I CALL MY BOY UNIT.\NLIKE. TWO HOURS AGO.
Dialogue: 0.0:07:18.87.0:07:21.01.Default..0.0.0..I'M LIKE. "DOG. THEY'RE MAKING\NME LOOK OUT TO BE A LIAR."
Dialogue: 0.0:07:21.04.0:07:22.71.Default..0.0.0..HE'S LIKE. "YO.\NI'LL CALL JIONNI RIGHT NOW.
Dialogue: 0.0:07:22.74.0:07:24.15.Default..0.0.0..WHAT'S HIS NUMBER?"
Dialogue: 0.0:07:24.17.0:07:26.38.Default..0.0.0..I GOT JIONNI'S NUMBER\NOUT THE PHONE BOOK AND GAVE IT.
Dialogue: 0.0:07:26.41.0:07:27.82.Default..0.0.0..REALLY. MIKE. THOUGH?
Dialogue: 0.0:07:27.84.0:07:30.02.Default..0.0.0..I'M NOT GONNA BE MADE\NTO LOOK LIKE A LIAR.
Dialogue: 0.0:07:30.05.0:07:32.29.Default..0.0.0..OH. MY GOD.\NI'M GONNA FLIP THE FUCK OUT.
Dialogue: 0.0:07:32.31.0:07:33.79.Default..0.0.0..YOU KNOW\NI'M TELLING HER. THOUGH.
Dialogue: 0.0:07:33.82.0:07:35.09.Default..0.0.0..YEAH. I GOT TO\NTELL HER THAT.
Dialogue: 0.0:07:35.12.0:07:36.83.Default..0.0.0..YOU GUYS CAN TELL HER.\NTHAT'S FUCKED UP.
Dialogue: 0.0:07:36.85.0:07:38.06.Default..0.0.0..THAT'S FUCKED UP.
Dialogue: 0.0:07:38.09.0:07:39.30.Default..0.0.0..DON'T MAKE ME LOOK\NTO BE A LIAR.
Dialogue: 0.0:07:39.32.0:07:40.53.Default..0.0.0..YEAH. BUT THAT'S\NYOUR FRIEND.
Dialogue: 0.0:07:40.56.0:07:42.00.Default..0.0.0..SO WHY IS SHE TELLING ME.\N"I HATE YOU.
Dialogue: 0.0:07:42.02.0:07:43.33.Default..0.0.0..DON'T EVER TALK\NTO ME AGAIN"?
Dialogue: 0.0:07:43.36.0:07:45.27.Default..0.0.0..YOU NEED TO TALK TO HER.\NBUT YOU SHOULD TALK TO HER
Dialogue: 0.0:07:45.29.0:07:46.47.Default..0.0.0..BEFORE YOU GO TO THAT LEVEL
Dialogue: 0.0:07:46.49.0:07:48.27.Default..0.0.0..OF CALLING YOUR FRIEND\NTO CALL HER BOYFRIEND.
Dialogue: 0.0:07:48.30.0:07:49.74.Default..0.0.0..THAT'S FUCKED UP.\NTHAT'S A DICK MOVE.
Dialogue: 0.0:07:49.77.0:07:51.01.Default..0.0.0..THAT'S FUCKED UP.
Dialogue: 0.0:07:51.03.0:07:52.81.Default..0.0.0..I'M NOT THE ONE THAT CHEATED\NON MY BOYFRIEND.
Dialogue: 0.0:07:52.83.0:07:53.98.Default..0.0.0..SHE DID.\NOH. MY GOD. I'M OUT.
Dialogue: 0.0:07:54.00.0:07:55.48.Default..0.0.0..I CAN'T DEAL\NWITH THIS SHIT.
Dialogue: 0.0:07:55.50.0:07:57.68.Default..0.0.0..IF YOU LOVE YOUR BOYFRIEND.\NYOU WOULDN'T HAVE {...} ME.
Dialogue: 0.0:07:57.71.0:07:59.75.Default..0.0.0..I DON'T KNOW WHAT'S\NGOING ON IN MIKE'S TWISTED HEAD.
Dialogue: 0.0:07:59.77.0:08:02.25.Default..0.0.0..HE HAD A REALLY GOOD CONNECTION\NWITH NICOLE; THEY WERE FRIENDS.
Dialogue: 0.0:08:02.28.0:08:04.06.Default..0.0.0..I'M MINDING MY BUSINESS.\NI DON'T GIVE A SHIT.
Dialogue: 0.0:08:04.08.0:08:06.42.Default..0.0.0..I FEEL LIKE THAT'S FUCKED UP.\NFRIENDS DON'T DO THAT.
Dialogue: 0.0:08:06.45.0:08:08.76.Default..0.0.0..PEOPLE WHO LOVE ONE ANOTHER\NDON'T DO THAT.
Dialogue: 0.0:08:12.75.0:08:14.50.Default..0.0.0..MIKE CALLED THE UNIT\NTO CALL JIONNI
Dialogue: 0.0:08:14.52.0:08:16.37.Default..0.0.0..AND TELL HIM EVERYTHING\NTHAT FUCKING HAPPENED
Dialogue: 0.0:08:16.39.0:08:17.60.Default..0.0.0..WITH YOU AND MIKE.
Dialogue: 0.0:08:17.63.0:08:18.80.Default..0.0.0..FUCK YOU. MIKE!
Dialogue: 0.0:08:18.83.0:08:19.87.Default..0.0.0..MIKE. I'M NOT KIDDING!
Dialogue: 0.0:08:20.93.0:08:22.04.Default..0.0.0..NICOLE!
Dialogue: 0.0:08:22.06.0:08:23.54.Default..0.0.0..DID YOU HOOK UP WITH HIM?\NYES.
Dialogue: 0.0:08:23.56.0:08:25.34.Default..0.0.0..TELL VINNY. WHEN I SEE HIM.\NHE'S DEAD.
Dialogue: 0.0:08:25.37.0:08:27.37.Default..0.0.0..HE'S DONE.\NNO. PLEASE DON'T.
Dialogue: 0.0:08:31.57.0:08:33.59.Default..0.0.0..{\i1}- BONGIORNO.\NBONGIORNO.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:08:33.61.0:08:36.22.Default..0.0.0..{\i1}BONGIORNO!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:08:36.25.0:08:37.89.Default..0.0.0..I'M STOPPING TRAFFIC.
Dialogue: 0.0:08:39.58.0:08:41.53.Default..0.0.0..WHEN PEOPLE FUNCTION\NIN THE MORNING THIS EARLY.
Dialogue: 0.0:08:41.55.0:08:43.33.Default..0.0.0..THIS ISN'T\NREAL LIFE TO ME.
Dialogue: 0.0:08:43.35.0:08:44.53.Default..0.0.0..IT'S LIKE\NIT'S A VIDEO GAME.
Dialogue: 0.0:08:44.55.0:08:47.49.Default..0.0.0..OH. MY GOD.\NI JUST SAW A NUN!
Dialogue: 0.0:08:50.76.0:08:53.24.Default..0.0.0..{\i1}CIAO!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:08:53.26.0:08:55.07.Default..0.0.0..I'VE NEVER SEEN\NA NUN BEFORE.
Dialogue: 0.0:08:55.10.0:08:57.86.Default..0.0.0..SHE IS SCARED\NFUCKIN' SHITLESS OF YOU.
Dialogue: 0.0:08:59.83.0:09:00.81.Default..0.0.0..OH. MY GOD.
Dialogue: 0.0:09:00.84.0:09:01.81.Default..0.0.0..IS THAT REAL?
Dialogue: 0.0:09:01.84.0:09:02.81.Default..0.0.0..YEAH.
Dialogue: 0.0:09:02.84.0:09:03.85.Default..0.0.0..I'LL BUY IT OFF YOU.
Dialogue: 0.0:09:03.87.0:09:05.62.Default..0.0.0..THIS IS VERY OLD WINE.
Dialogue: 0.0:09:05.64.0:09:06.65.Default..0.0.0..AWESOME.
Dialogue: 0.0:09:06.68.0:09:08.82.Default..0.0.0..HOW ARE WE GONNA\NGET THIS HOME?
Dialogue: 0.0:09:08.84.0:09:10.82.Default..0.0.0..-{\i1} GRAZIE.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:09:10.85.0:09:12.32.Default..0.0.0..JENNI. LOOK WHAT I GOT.
Dialogue: 0.0:09:12.35.0:09:14.39.Default..0.0.0..A 1981.\NLOOK AT.
Dialogue: 0.0:09:14.42.0:09:15.79.Default..0.0.0..WOW!
Dialogue: 0.0:09:15.82.0:09:18.80.Default..0.0.0..SO NICOLE BUYS THIS. LIKE.\N20-GALLON THING OF CHIANTI.
Dialogue: 0.0:09:18.82.0:09:21.87.Default..0.0.0..AND WE'RE WALKING DOWN\NTHE FUCKING COBBLESTONE STREET.
Dialogue: 0.0:09:21.89.0:09:23.43.Default..0.0.0..NICOLE. YOU'RE GONNA RIP IT.
Dialogue: 0.0:09:23.46.0:09:25.24.Default..0.0.0..OH. MY GOD!
Dialogue: 0.0:09:25.26.0:09:27.84.Default..0.0.0..OH. MY GOD.\NOH. MY GOD.
Dialogue: 0.0:09:27.86.0:09:30.51.Default..0.0.0..OH. MY GOD.\NOH. MY GOD.
Dialogue: 0.0:09:30.53.0:09:33.01.Default..0.0.0..OH. MY GOD.\NMY GOD. NO!
Dialogue: 0.0:09:33.04.0:09:36.08.Default..0.0.0..ALL OF A SUDDEN. THIS BOTTLE\NOF WINE SMASHES EVERYWHERE.
Dialogue: 0.0:09:37.11.0:09:39.78.Default..0.0.0..OH. MY GOD!\NNO!
Dialogue: 0.0:09:39.81.0:09:42.72.Default..0.0.0..NO. NO!
Dialogue: 0.0:09:42.74.0:09:43.89.Default..0.0.0..{\i1}COME SI DICE.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:09:43.91.0:09:45.89.Default..0.0.0..THIS FUCKING SUCKS BALLS!
Dialogue: 0.0:09:50.85.0:09:52.30.Default..0.0.0..HELLO?
Dialogue: 0.0:09:52.32.0:09:53.40.Default..0.0.0..MA.
Dialogue: 0.0:09:53.42.0:09:54.53.Default..0.0.0..HI.
Dialogue: 0.0:09:54.56.0:09:56.40.Default..0.0.0..HI. GUESS WHERE\NI'M GOING TUESDAY.
Dialogue: 0.0:09:56.42.0:09:57.70.Default..0.0.0..SO WHERE YOU\NGOING. VIN?
Dialogue: 0.0:09:57.73.0:09:59.20.Default..0.0.0..SICILY.
Dialogue: 0.0:09:59.23.0:10:01.31.Default..0.0.0..ME AND. UH.\NTHE BOYS ARE GOING.
Dialogue: 0.0:10:01.33.0:10:02.57.Default..0.0.0..WOW. VIN.
Dialogue: 0.0:10:02.60.0:10:05.01.Default..0.0.0..WE ARE GOING TO SICILY.\NJUST THE BOYS.
Dialogue: 0.0:10:05.03.0:10:06.54.Default..0.0.0..WE'RE TAKING A TRIP\NTO VISIT MY FAMILY
Dialogue: 0.0:10:06.57.0:10:09.48.Default..0.0.0..AND SEE MY MOTHER'S TOWN\NWHERE SHE WAS BORN.
Dialogue: 0.0:10:09.50.0:10:12.98.Default..0.0.0..THIS IS WHAT I'VE WANTED\NTO DO MY WHOLE LIFE.
Dialogue: 0.0:10:13.01.0:10:15.79.Default..0.0.0..PAULY WANTS TO KNOW IF THERE ARE\NANY YOUNG GIRL COUSINS FOR HIM.
Dialogue: 0.0:10:17.18.0:10:18.19.Default..0.0.0..HELLO?\NHELLO?
Dialogue: 0.0:10:18.21.0:10:20.02.Default..0.0.0..ARE YOU THERE?\NMA?
Dialogue: 0.0:10:26.79.0:10:28.27.Default..0.0.0..WHAT'S THE MATTER?
Dialogue: 0.0:10:28.29.0:10:31.52.Default..0.0.0..OH. OH. OH!
Dialogue: 0.0:10:33.60.0:10:35.37.Default..0.0.0..YOU GUYS WANT\NTO GET SOME FOOD OR SOMETHING?
Dialogue: 0.0:10:35.40.0:10:37.64.Default..0.0.0..I GOT TO DO LAUNDRY.
Dialogue: 0.0:10:37.67.0:10:39.44.Default..0.0.0..I DON'T FEEL GOOD.
Dialogue: 0.0:10:39.47.0:10:43.28.Default..0.0.0..AS A JOKE.\NI GO UP TO RONNIE...
Dialogue: 0.0:10:43.30.0:10:46.48.Default..0.0.0..I GO "RONNIE. MAN.\NI CALLED MY BOY UNIT UP...
Dialogue: 0.0:10:46.51.0:10:49.22.Default..0.0.0.."GAVE HIM\NJIONNI'S NUMBER...
Dialogue: 0.0:10:49.24.0:10:51.59.Default..0.0.0..AND TOLD HIM TO CALL JIONNI\NAND TELL HIM THE DEAL."
Dialogue: 0.0:10:51.61.0:10:52.72.Default..0.0.0..NO. YOU DIDN'T.
Dialogue: 0.0:10:52.75.0:10:56.13.Default..0.0.0..I DIDN'T.\NBUT I TOLD RONNIE I DID.
Dialogue: 0.0:10:56.15.0:11:00.16.Default..0.0.0..NOW. BEFORE RONNIE\NEVEN LEFT THE HOUSE.
Dialogue: 0.0:11:00.19.0:11:01.93.Default..0.0.0..HE HAD ALREADY TOLD SAM.
Dialogue: 0.0:11:05.09.0:11:07.67.Default..0.0.0..BUT I REALLY DIDN'T\NCALL JIONNI.
Dialogue: 0.0:11:07.70.0:11:09.34.Default..0.0.0..THAT'S BRILLIANT.
Dialogue: 0.0:11:10.80.0:11:14.75.Default..0.0.0..NOW IT'S LIKE.\N"GYM. TAN. WHO'S THE RAT?"
Dialogue: 0.0:11:14.77.0:11:16.08.Default..0.0.0..I DON'T UNDERSTAND\NTHE DRAMA.
Dialogue: 0.0:11:16.10.0:11:17.65.Default..0.0.0..WHATEVER MIKE'S\NINTENTIONS WERE.
Dialogue: 0.0:11:17.67.0:11:20.28.Default..0.0.0..BUT I'M JUST SITTING HERE\NWITH MY POPCORN IN MY HAND
Dialogue: 0.0:11:20.31.0:11:22.29.Default..0.0.0..WAITING FOR THIS SHIT\NTO POP OFF.
Dialogue: 0.0:11:22.31.0:11:24.52.Default..0.0.0..IT'S GONNA BE\NA SHIT SHOW TONIGHT.
Dialogue: 0.0:11:24.55.0:11:27.29.Default..0.0.0..NO. IT'S GONNA BE BAD.
Dialogue: 0.0:11:27.32.0:11:29.53.Default..0.0.0..OH. MY GOD.
Dialogue: 0.0:11:29.55.0:11:31.83.Default..0.0.0..WORK IS OVER ALREADY?
Dialogue: 0.0:11:31.85.0:11:33.09.Default..0.0.0..OH. MY GOD.
Dialogue: 0.0:11:37.69.0:11:39.70.Default..0.0.0..NICOLE.
Dialogue: 0.0:11:39.73.0:11:42.51.Default..0.0.0..I AM SO UPSET ABOUT WHAT MIKE\NSAID THIS MORNING
Dialogue: 0.0:11:42.53.0:11:44.38.Default..0.0.0..THAT I'M LIKE.\NNICOLE NEEDS TO KNOW THIS.
Dialogue: 0.0:11:44.40.0:11:45.98.Default..0.0.0..THAT WAS THE LOWEST SHIT\NI'VE EVER HEARD.
Dialogue: 0.0:11:46.00.0:11:48.05.Default..0.0.0..I'VE GOTTA TELL YOU\NWHAT THE FUCK JUST HAPPENED.
Dialogue: 0.0:11:48.07.0:11:49.68.Default..0.0.0..THEY CALLED THE UNIT\NTO CALL JIONNI
Dialogue: 0.0:11:49.70.0:11:51.52.Default..0.0.0..AND TELL HIM EVERYTHING\NTHAT FUCKING HAPPENED
Dialogue: 0.0:11:51.54.0:11:53.47.Default..0.0.0..WITH YOU AND MIKE.
Dialogue: 0.0:11:59.48.0:12:02.79.Default..0.0.0..STOP GETTING IN MY BUSINESS.\NYOU MOTHERFUCKER!
Dialogue: 0.0:12:02.82.0:12:05.03.Default..0.0.0..STOP FUCKING GETTING\NIN MY BUSINESS. YOU FUCKER!
Dialogue: 0.0:12:05.05.0:12:06.86.Default..0.0.0..YOU IN THE HOUSE-\NAND FUCKING STOP!
Dialogue: 0.0:12:06.89.0:12:09.47.Default..0.0.0..STOP!\NI'M NOT EVEN KIDDING. MIKE!
Dialogue: 0.0:12:09.49.0:12:11.27.Default..0.0.0..FUCK YOU!\NFUCK YOU!
Dialogue: 0.0:12:11.29.0:12:13.54.Default..0.0.0..FUCK YOU!\NYOU FUCKING BITCH.
Dialogue: 0.0:12:13.56.0:12:16.51.Default..0.0.0..FUCK YOU!\NFUCK YOU!
Dialogue: 0.0:12:16.53.0:12:19.04.Default..0.0.0..FUCK YOU.\NFUCK YOU. MIKE.
Dialogue: 0.0:12:19.07.0:12:20.95.Default..0.0.0..MIKE. I'M NOT KIDDING!
Dialogue: 0.0:12:20.97.0:12:22.95.Default..0.0.0..NICOLE!\NNICOLE.
Dialogue: 0.0:12:22.97.0:12:25.05.Default..0.0.0..DON'T SIT HERE\NAND FEED PEOPLE LIES.
Dialogue: 0.0:12:25.07.0:12:27.28.Default..0.0.0..YOU'RE FEEDING EVERYBODY\NIN THIS HOUSE YOUR LIES.
Dialogue: 0.0:12:27.31.0:12:28.82.Default..0.0.0..MAYBE NICOLE\NISN'T BEING HONEST.
Dialogue: 0.0:12:28.84.0:12:31.58.Default..0.0.0..MAYBE MIKE'S TELLING\NTHE TRUTH ABOUT YOUR STORY.
Dialogue: 0.0:12:32.95.0:12:34.23.Default..0.0.0..FUCK YOU.\NFUCK YOU.
Dialogue: 0.0:12:34.25.0:12:37.83.Default..0.0.0..FUCK YOU.\NYOU FUCKING BITCH.
Dialogue: 0.0:12:37.85.0:12:40.77.Default..0.0.0..FUCK YOU.\NFUCK YOU. MIKE.
Dialogue: 0.0:12:40.79.0:12:42.63.Default..0.0.0..MIKE. I'M NOT KIDDING!
Dialogue: 0.0:12:42.66.0:12:44.10.Default..0.0.0..WHOA.\NNICOLE.
Dialogue: 0.0:12:44.13.0:12:46.00.Default..0.0.0..FUCK YOU.
Dialogue: 0.0:12:46.03.0:12:47.20.Default..0.0.0..NICOLE.\NFUCK YOU. MIKE.
Dialogue: 0.0:12:47.23.0:12:49.41.Default..0.0.0..FUCK YOU.\NYOU'RE FUCKING DEAD.
Dialogue: 0.0:12:49.43.0:12:51.14.Default..0.0.0..YOU'RE NOT FUCKING\NPART OF THIS HOUSE.
Dialogue: 0.0:12:51.17.0:12:53.01.Default..0.0.0..MIKE'S DODGING EVERYTHING\NLIKE THE MATRIX.
Dialogue: 0.0:12:53.03.0:12:54.44.Default..0.0.0..SHE'S THROWIN'\NWINE BOTTLES AT HIM.
Dialogue: 0.0:12:54.47.0:12:55.81.Default..0.0.0..HE'S DUCKING 'EM.
Dialogue: 0.0:12:55.84.0:12:57.68.Default..0.0.0..HE'S MOVING ALL AROUND.\NHE'S RUNNING FROM HER.
Dialogue: 0.0:12:57.71.0:12:59.68.Default..0.0.0..FUCK YOU.\NFUCK YOU.
Dialogue: 0.0:12:59.71.0:13:00.68.Default..0.0.0..WHAT?\NWHAT?
Dialogue: 0.0:13:00.71.0:13:01.75.Default..0.0.0..FUCK YOU.
Dialogue: 0.0:13:01.78.0:13:03.09.Default..0.0.0..WHY THE FUCK\NWOULD YOU TELL UNIT
Dialogue: 0.0:13:03.11.0:13:04.59.Default..0.0.0..TO FUCKING CALL JIONNI?
Dialogue: 0.0:13:04.61.0:13:05.72.Default..0.0.0..I DIDN'T DO NOTHIN'.
Dialogue: 0.0:13:05.75.0:13:07.32.Default..0.0.0..WHY?\NWHAT IS YOUR PROBLEM?
Dialogue: 0.0:13:07.35.0:13:08.49.Default..0.0.0..YOU WANNA KNOW WHAT I DID?
Dialogue: 0.0:13:08.52.0:13:10.50.Default..0.0.0..SAY WHAT YOU DID. MIKE.
Dialogue: 0.0:13:10.52.0:13:13.16.Default..0.0.0..SAM OVERHEARD ME SAY...
Dialogue: 0.0:13:13.19.0:13:15.87.Default..0.0.0..DO NOT DO ANYTHING. I'LL...
Dialogue: 0.0:13:15.89.0:13:17.74.Default..0.0.0..WILL YOU LISTEN TO ME\NBEFORE I SPEAK?
Dialogue: 0.0:13:17.76.0:13:19.80.Default..0.0.0..I DON'T LIKE YOU.\NI DON'T FUCKIN' LIKE YOU.
Dialogue: 0.0:13:19.83.0:13:21.04.Default..0.0.0..I DON'T FUCKING LIKE YOU.
Dialogue: 0.0:13:21.06.0:13:22.74.Default..0.0.0..NICOLE.\NI DON'T FUCKING LIKE YOU.
Dialogue: 0.0:13:22.76.0:13:24.41.Default..0.0.0..I DON'T FUCKIN' LIKE YOU.\NNICOLE. WAIT.
Dialogue: 0.0:13:24.43.0:13:25.41.Default..0.0.0..I FUCKING HATE YOU.
Dialogue: 0.0:13:25.43.0:13:26.58.Default..0.0.0..NICOLE. JUST-\NI HATE YOU.
Dialogue: 0.0:13:26.60.0:13:27.85.Default..0.0.0..HE DIDN'T DO ANYTHING.\NNO.
Dialogue: 0.0:13:27.87.0:13:29.31.Default..0.0.0..HE DIDN'T DO IT.\NHE'S... IT WAS A JOKE.
Dialogue: 0.0:13:29.34.0:13:30.51.Default..0.0.0..I DIDN'T DO IT!\NIT WAS A JOKE.
Dialogue: 0.0:13:30.54.0:13:31.75.Default..0.0.0..HE DIDN'T DO IT.\NIT WAS A JOKE!
Dialogue: 0.0:13:31.77.0:13:33.08.Default..0.0.0..THAT'S NOT\NA FUNNY FUCKING JOKE.
Dialogue: 0.0:13:33.11.0:13:34.49.Default..0.0.0..WHO WOULD FUCKING\NSAY THAT. THEN?
Dialogue: 0.0:13:34.51.0:13:35.82.Default..0.0.0..IT WAS A JOKE!\NTHAT'S NOT FUNNY!
Dialogue: 0.0:13:35.84.0:13:37.15.Default..0.0.0..WELL. YOU NEED TO ASK\NSOMEBODY.
Dialogue: 0.0:13:37.18.0:13:39.02.Default..0.0.0..DON'T LISTEN\NFROM THE PEANUT GALLERY.
Dialogue: 0.0:13:39.05.0:13:40.36.Default..0.0.0..ASK PEOPLE FIRST!
Dialogue: 0.0:13:40.38.0:13:42.06.Default..0.0.0..'CAUSE I DIDN'T MAKE\NNO FUCKING PHONE CALL.
Dialogue: 0.0:13:42.08.0:13:43.73.Default..0.0.0..THEN WHY WOULD YOU GO AROUND\NSAYIN' THAT?
Dialogue: 0.0:13:43.75.0:13:45.13.Default..0.0.0..WHY ARE YOU FUCKING\NTALKIN' SHIT?
Dialogue: 0.0:13:45.15.0:13:46.73.Default..0.0.0..STAY OUT OF IT!\NWHY WOULD YOU SAY THAT?
Dialogue: 0.0:13:46.76.0:13:48.83.Default..0.0.0..LET HER ASK FIRST!\NWHY WOULD YOU SAY THAT TO ME?
Dialogue: 0.0:13:48.86.0:13:51.27.Default..0.0.0..LET HER ASK FIRST!\NDON'T LOOK AT ME. NICOLE!
Dialogue: 0.0:13:51.29.0:13:52.50.Default..0.0.0..HE FUCKING SAID IT!
Dialogue: 0.0:13:52.53.0:13:54.87.Default..0.0.0..NO PHONE CALL WAS EVER MADE!\NHE SAID IT!
Dialogue: 0.0:13:54.90.0:13:57.14.Default..0.0.0..I WAS FOOLIN' AROUND\NBECAUSE. GUESS WHAT.
Dialogue: 0.0:13:57.17.0:13:58.41.Default..0.0.0..YOU TALKED TO EVERYBODY FIRST.
Dialogue: 0.0:13:58.43.0:14:01.11.Default..0.0.0..AND IT BACKFIRED ON YOU.
Dialogue: 0.0:14:01.14.0:14:03.75.Default..0.0.0..HE'S A FUCKING DICK.
Dialogue: 0.0:14:03.77.0:14:07.02.Default..0.0.0..MIKE IS TRYING TO PROVE\NTHAT ME AND DEENA ARE RATS.
Dialogue: 0.0:14:07.04.0:14:08.35.Default..0.0.0..LIKE. WHAT DO YOU MEAN "RATS"?
Dialogue: 0.0:14:08.38.0:14:10.19.Default..0.0.0..LIKE. WHAT'S COMING\NOUT OF YOUR MOUTH RIGHT NOW
Dialogue: 0.0:14:10.21.0:14:11.22.Default..0.0.0..IS STRAIGHT BULLSHIT.
Dialogue: 0.0:14:11.25.0:14:13.79.Default..0.0.0..I DIDN'T DO NOTHIN'!
Dialogue: 0.0:14:13.82.0:14:14.93.Default..0.0.0..NOTHING.
Dialogue: 0.0:14:14.95.0:14:17.36.Default..0.0.0..ALL I DID WAS TELL THREE PEOPLE\NA LITTLE LIE
Dialogue: 0.0:14:17.39.0:14:20.06.Default..0.0.0..BECAUSE I WANTED TO SEE\NWHO WOULD RAT WHO OUT.
Dialogue: 0.0:14:20.09.0:14:21.23.Default..0.0.0..AND GUESS WHAT HAPPENED.
Dialogue: 0.0:14:21.26.0:14:23.17.Default..0.0.0..SAM'S THE ONE\NWHO RATTED HERSELF OUT.
Dialogue: 0.0:14:23.19.0:14:24.90.Default..0.0.0..SHE IMMEDIATELY RAN IN THE ROOM\NAND RATTED.
Dialogue: 0.0:14:24.93.0:14:26.74.Default..0.0.0..I DIDN'T DO ANYTHING. SNOOKI.
Dialogue: 0.0:14:26.76.0:14:28.24.Default..0.0.0..GO AWAY!
Dialogue: 0.0:14:28.26.0:14:30.61.Default..0.0.0..LEAVE ME ALONE.
Dialogue: 0.0:14:30.63.0:14:32.91.Default..0.0.0..I DIDN'T DO ANYTHING TO YOU.\NOKAY?
Dialogue: 0.0:14:32.93.0:14:34.45.Default..0.0.0..GET THE FUCK AWAY FROM ME!\NI CAN'T...
Dialogue: 0.0:14:34.47.0:14:37.95.Default..0.0.0..FUCKING SOMEWHERE. JUST GO!\NGET AWAY FROM ME.
Dialogue: 0.0:14:37.97.0:14:40.82.Default..0.0.0..FUCKING SMILE ON YOUR FACE...\NYOU'RE A FUCKING BITCH.
Dialogue: 0.0:14:40.84.0:14:43.32.Default..0.0.0..SMILE ON MY FACE... HOW ABOUT I\NMAKE THAT PHONE CALL RIGHT NOW?
Dialogue: 0.0:14:43.35.0:14:44.46.Default..0.0.0..GET AWAY FROM ME!
Dialogue: 0.0:14:44.48.0:14:45.86.Default..0.0.0..HOW ABOUT I MAKE\NA REAL PHONE CALL?
Dialogue: 0.0:14:45.88.0:14:47.49.Default..0.0.0..GET AWAY FROM ME!
Dialogue: 0.0:14:47.52.0:14:52.16.Default..0.0.0..HOW ABOUT I MAKE THE REAL-\NGET AWAY!
Dialogue: 0.0:14:56.22.0:15:00.30.Default..0.0.0..IS SHE CRYING?\NSHE'S CRYING.
Dialogue: 0.0:15:00.33.0:15:02.31.Default..0.0.0..SHE'S CRYING OVER IT\NBECAUSE SHE KNOWS IT'S TRUE.
Dialogue: 0.0:15:02.33.0:15:04.51.Default..0.0.0..BUT I DIDN'T SAY ANYTHING.
Dialogue: 0.0:15:04.53.0:15:05.84.Default..0.0.0..YEAH. BUT BY YOU\NMAKING BELIEVE.
Dialogue: 0.0:15:05.87.0:15:07.14.Default..0.0.0..IT'S THE SAME EFFECT.
Dialogue: 0.0:15:07.17.0:15:08.45.Default..0.0.0..I UNDERSTAND THAT. BUT...
Dialogue: 0.0:15:08.47.0:15:10.31.Default..0.0.0..DIDN'T NEED TO PROVE\NYOU SAID IT.
Dialogue: 0.0:15:10.34.0:15:12.28.Default..0.0.0..ALL SHE HAD TO DO WAS.\N"MIKE. DID YOU MAKE A CALL?"
Dialogue: 0.0:15:12.31.0:15:13.35.Default..0.0.0.."NOPE. DIDN'T."
Dialogue: 0.0:15:13.38.0:15:14.49.Default..0.0.0..AND IT WOULD'VE BEEN SOLVED.
Dialogue: 0.0:15:14.51.0:15:16.72.Default..0.0.0..INSTEAD. SHE JUST WENT\NFLIPPIN' OUT.
Dialogue: 0.0:15:16.75.0:15:18.09.Default..0.0.0..THROWING SHIT.\NFIGHTIN'.
Dialogue: 0.0:15:18.11.0:15:20.32.Default..0.0.0..AND THAT'S EXACTLY HOW\NIT HAPPENS IN THIS HOUSE
Dialogue: 0.0:15:20.35.0:15:21.32.Default..0.0.0..EVERY SINGLE TIME.
Dialogue: 0.0:15:21.35.0:15:22.53.Default..0.0.0..IT'S JUST MESSED UP
Dialogue: 0.0:15:22.55.0:15:24.43.Default..0.0.0..'CAUSE SHE REALLY CARES\NABOUT THE KID. YOU KNOW?
Dialogue: 0.0:15:24.45.0:15:25.56.Default..0.0.0..I KNOW.
Dialogue: 0.0:15:25.59.0:15:27.06.Default..0.0.0..IT LOOKED LIKE SHE CARED\NLAST NIGHT.
Dialogue: 0.0:15:30.66.0:15:32.37.Default..0.0.0..SNOOKI CAME INTO VINNY'S BED.
Dialogue: 0.0:15:32.39.0:15:33.50.Default..0.0.0..WANTIN' TO SMUSH WITH VINNY.
Dialogue: 0.0:15:33.53.0:15:35.04.Default..0.0.0..SHE TOLD ME SHE WAS SINGLE\NLAST NIGHT.
Dialogue: 0.0:15:35.06.0:15:36.04.Default..0.0.0..SO I WAS LIKE. "ALL RIGHT."
Dialogue: 0.0:15:36.06.0:15:37.04.Default..0.0.0..THAT'S WHAT'S UP.
Dialogue: 0.0:15:37.07.0:15:38.28.Default..0.0.0..I'VE ROOMED WITH\NVINNY BEFORE.
Dialogue: 0.0:15:38.30.0:15:39.88.Default..0.0.0..I KNOW WHAT IT SOUNDS LIKE\NWHEN HE GETS IN.
Dialogue: 0.0:15:39.90.0:15:41.15.Default..0.0.0..I KNOW WHAT GOES DOWN.
Dialogue: 0.0:15:41.17.0:15:44.47.Default..0.0.0..AND. UM. THEY GOT IT IN.
Dialogue: 0.0:15:51.31.0:15:55.39.Default..0.0.0..THIS IS DEFINITELY MY MOST\NWELL-THOUGHT-OUT EVIL PLAN.
Dialogue: 0.0:15:55.42.0:15:57.92.Default..0.0.0..BUT THE PRANK THAT I PULLED\NWAS A NECESSARY EVIL.
Dialogue: 0.0:16:01.79.0:16:02.93.Default..0.0.0..I'M OVER THIS.
Dialogue: 0.0:16:02.96.0:16:04.87.Default..0.0.0..JENNI!
Dialogue: 0.0:16:04.89.0:16:08.34.Default..0.0.0..YEAH?\NCOME HERE.
Dialogue: 0.0:16:08.36.0:16:11.98.Default..0.0.0..WHAT'S WRONG?
Dialogue: 0.0:16:12.00.0:16:15.41.Default..0.0.0..THIS IS NOT FUN ANYMORE.
Dialogue: 0.0:16:15.44.0:16:17.85.Default..0.0.0..HONESTLY. I GAVE MIKE\NA COUPLE CHANCES. I FEEL. HERE.
Dialogue: 0.0:16:17.87.0:16:19.32.Default..0.0.0..BUT. AT THIS POINT.
Dialogue: 0.0:16:19.34.0:16:21.49.Default..0.0.0..WHEN YOU FUCK WITH ME LIKE THAT.\NIT'S DONE.
Dialogue: 0.0:16:21.51.0:16:22.55.Default..0.0.0..AND AS OF RIGHT NOW.
Dialogue: 0.0:16:22.58.0:16:23.95.Default..0.0.0..I AM DONE WITH MIKE.
Dialogue: 0.0:16:23.98.0:16:25.16.Default..0.0.0..OVER IT.\NDONE.
Dialogue: 0.0:16:25.18.0:16:26.69.Default..0.0.0..HE'S A SICK FUCKIN' KID.
Dialogue: 0.0:16:26.71.0:16:28.86.Default..0.0.0..I'VE BEEN TELLIN' YOU\NTHAT SINCE DAY FUCKIN' ONE.
Dialogue: 0.0:16:28.88.0:16:30.99.Default..0.0.0..HE'S A SICK FUCKIN' KID.
Dialogue: 0.0:16:31.02.0:16:32.30.Default..0.0.0..BEEN SAYIN' THAT\NSINCE DAY ONE.
Dialogue: 0.0:16:32.32.0:16:34.07.Default..0.0.0..AND NOBODY WANTED\NTO LISTEN TO ME.
Dialogue: 0.0:16:34.09.0:16:36.17.Default..0.0.0..EVERYONE THOUGHT I WAS\NTHE CRAZY ONE.
Dialogue: 0.0:16:36.19.0:16:38.00.Default..0.0.0..I NEVER LIKED THE KID. RON.
Dialogue: 0.0:16:38.03.0:16:40.07.Default..0.0.0..HE'S A SICK FUCKING\NINDIVIDUAL.
Dialogue: 0.0:16:40.09.0:16:42.57.Default..0.0.0..I DON'T REALLY KNOW WHAT\NHAPPENED WITH MIKE AND NICOLE.
Dialogue: 0.0:16:42.60.0:16:44.01.Default..0.0.0..WHO CARES IF THEY FUCKING\NHOOKED UP?
Dialogue: 0.0:16:44.03.0:16:45.88.Default..0.0.0..IF YOU'RE FRIENDS.\NYOU DON'T FUCKING
Dialogue: 0.0:16:45.90.0:16:47.68.Default..0.0.0..PULL SHIT\NLIKE YOU FUCKING PULLED.
Dialogue: 0.0:16:47.70.0:16:49.95.Default..0.0.0..RIDICULOUS.
Dialogue: 0.0:16:49.97.0:16:52.02.Default..0.0.0..THIS WAS A-\NTHIS WAS A TEST.
Dialogue: 0.0:16:52.04.0:16:53.62.Default..0.0.0..A BROADCAST SYSTEM TEST.
Dialogue: 0.0:16:53.64.0:16:55.69.Default..0.0.0..YOU WOULD THINK HE WOULD LEARN\NTO STOP AFTER A WHILE
Dialogue: 0.0:16:55.71.0:16:57.15.Default..0.0.0..BECAUSE HE GOT PUNCHED\NIN THE FACE.
Dialogue: 0.0:16:57.18.0:16:58.69.Default..0.0.0..HE RAN INTO A WALL.
Dialogue: 0.0:16:58.71.0:17:00.99.Default..0.0.0..AND NOW HE'S GETTING CHAMPAGNE\NBOTTLES THROWN AT HIS HEAD.
Dialogue: 0.0:17:01.02.0:17:03.19.Default..0.0.0..HOW MANY WAKE-UP CALLS\NDOES MIKE NEED?
Dialogue: 0.0:17:03.22.0:17:04.63.Default..0.0.0..DOESN'T MATTER.\NTHAT IS HUGE.
Dialogue: 0.0:17:04.65.0:17:06.13.Default..0.0.0..BECAUSE I WANTED\NTO BE DONE WITH HIM.
Dialogue: 0.0:17:06.15.0:17:07.13.Default..0.0.0..WELL. YOU ARE NOW.
Dialogue: 0.0:17:07.15.0:17:09.83.Default..0.0.0..HE IS GONE.\NSO ACCEPT IT.
Dialogue: 0.0:17:09.86.0:17:10.93.Default..0.0.0..AND MOVE ON.
Dialogue: 0.0:17:10.96.0:17:12.34.Default..0.0.0..CAN WE TALK ABOUT\NTHE OTHER NIGHT?
Dialogue: 0.0:17:12.36.0:17:14.10.Default..0.0.0..I WANNA KNOW WHAT HAPPENED\NWITH ME AND VINNY.
Dialogue: 0.0:17:14.13.0:17:15.31.Default..0.0.0..LIKE. DID WE HAVE SEX AND STUFF?
Dialogue: 0.0:17:15.33.0:17:17.61.Default..0.0.0..DID WE...
Dialogue: 0.0:17:17.63.0:17:19.00.Default..0.0.0..ALL RIGHT. LET'S GO OUTSIDE.
Dialogue: 0.0:17:29.31.0:17:32.19.Default..0.0.0..♪ WE'RE GOING TO SICILY TODAY.
Dialogue: 0.0:17:32.21.0:17:33.36.Default..0.0.0..TIME TO WAKE UP.
Dialogue: 0.0:17:33.38.0:17:36.09.Default..0.0.0..YEAH. BUDDY.\NYEAH. BUDDY.
Dialogue: 0.0:17:36.12.0:17:38.43.Default..0.0.0..NICOLE.\NGET UP!
Dialogue: 0.0:17:38.45.0:17:40.26.Default..0.0.0..HERE.
Dialogue: 0.0:17:40.29.0:17:41.97.Default..0.0.0..THIS MIGHT MAKE YOU\NFEEL BETTER.
Dialogue: 0.0:17:41.99.0:17:44.47.Default..0.0.0..WE'RE GONNA GO TO A WINE THING.\NJUST US GIRLS.
Dialogue: 0.0:17:44.49.0:17:46.44.Default..0.0.0..AFTER ALL THE DRAMA\NTHAT JUST HAPPENED WITH MIKE.
Dialogue: 0.0:17:46.46.0:17:49.37.Default..0.0.0..THIS TIME COULDN'T\NHAVE CAME MORE PERFECT.
Dialogue: 0.0:17:49.40.0:17:51.14.Default..0.0.0..THE BOYS ARE GOING TO SICILY.
Dialogue: 0.0:17:51.17.0:17:54.38.Default..0.0.0..SO WE DECIDED WE'RE GOING\NTO TUSCANY ON A WINE TOUR.
Dialogue: 0.0:17:54.40.0:17:56.21.Default..0.0.0..WE'RE GONNA DRINK SOME WINE.\NGET SOME... DRUNK.
Dialogue: 0.0:17:56.24.0:17:58.88.Default..0.0.0..IT'S GONNA BE FUN.\NGOOD MORNING. BOO.
Dialogue: 0.0:17:58.91.0:18:00.15.Default..0.0.0..SHH.\NYOU SHH!
Dialogue: 0.0:18:00.17.0:18:02.42.Default..0.0.0..YOU'RE NOT RUINING\NTHIS FUCKING TRIP FOR US.
Dialogue: 0.0:18:02.44.0:18:03.62.Default..0.0.0..YOU HAVE TO GO.
Dialogue: 0.0:18:03.65.0:18:04.72.Default..0.0.0..YOU FUCK... DON'T.
Dialogue: 0.0:18:04.75.0:18:06.46.Default..0.0.0..I'LL PULL THE BLANKET\NRIGHT OFF.
Dialogue: 0.0:18:06.48.0:18:08.23.Default..0.0.0..YOU WENT TO BED\NBEFORE ME LAST NIGHT.
Dialogue: 0.0:18:08.25.0:18:09.69.Default..0.0.0..AND I'VE BEEN UP\NFOR 2 1/2 HOURS.
Dialogue: 0.0:18:09.72.0:18:11.63.Default..0.0.0..SHUT THE FUCK UP. JENNI.\NWE LEAVE IN 20 MINUTES.
Dialogue: 0.0:18:11.65.0:18:12.93.Default..0.0.0..I'M NOT GONNA SHUT UP.
Dialogue: 0.0:18:12.95.0:18:14.70.Default..0.0.0..I DON'T GIVE YOU ATTITUDE\NLIKE THIS WHEN I...
Dialogue: 0.0:18:14.72.0:18:16.53.Default..0.0.0..SHUT UP!\NHAVE TO GET YOU UP
Dialogue: 0.0:18:16.56.0:18:17.70.Default..0.0.0..OR I GET UP FOR YOU.
Dialogue: 0.0:18:17.73.0:18:18.94.Default..0.0.0..I UNDERSTAND.\NJUST SHUT UP.
Dialogue: 0.0:18:18.96.0:18:21.04.Default..0.0.0..PLEASE.\NJUST STOP TALKING TO ME.
Dialogue: 0.0:18:21.06.0:18:23.57.Default..0.0.0..DON'T WANNA GO\NTO THIS STUPID THING.
Dialogue: 0.0:18:23.60.0:18:25.20.Default..0.0.0..WELL. GOOD MORNING TO YOU.
Dialogue: 0.0:18:28.07.0:18:30.81.Default..0.0.0..WE LOOK SO SOPHISTICATED\NAND CLASSY.
Dialogue: 0.0:18:30.84.0:18:32.22.Default..0.0.0..RIGHT?\NEW!
Dialogue: 0.0:18:32.24.0:18:33.82.Default..0.0.0..NICOLE.\NWHAT?
Dialogue: 0.0:18:33.84.0:18:35.15.Default..0.0.0..DID YOU FART?\NYEAH.
Dialogue: 0.0:18:35.18.0:18:38.05.Default..0.0.0..UGH!\NOH. MY GOD. NICOLE.
Dialogue: 0.0:18:38.08.0:18:39.76.Default..0.0.0..AND THERE GOES OUR CLASS.
Dialogue: 0.0:18:43.18.0:18:44.56.Default..0.0.0..YOU'RE IN\NTHE SIXTH GRADE NOW?
Dialogue: 0.0:18:45.95.0:18:47.97.Default..0.0.0..I'M SO EXCITED\NTO MEET MY FAMILY
Dialogue: 0.0:18:47.99.0:18:49.03.Default..0.0.0..FOR THE FIRST TIME.
Dialogue: 0.0:18:49.06.0:18:50.43.Default..0.0.0..I'M PROUD TO BE SICILIAN.
Dialogue: 0.0:18:50.46.0:18:52.74.Default..0.0.0..AND THIS IS WHAT\NLIFE IS ALL ABOUT.
Dialogue: 0.0:18:52.76.0:18:55.47.Default..0.0.0..TRACING YOUR ROOTS\NAND GOING TO THE HOMELAND.
Dialogue: 0.0:18:55.50.0:18:58.53.Default..0.0.0..YEP.\NSICILY!
Dialogue: 0.0:19:11.68.0:19:13.02.Default..0.0.0..FUCKING SICILY.
Dialogue: 0.0:19:13.05.0:19:15.46.Default..0.0.0..OH. MY GOD.\NHOLY SHIT.
Dialogue: 0.0:19:15.48.0:19:18.83.Default..0.0.0..BOYS ARE PUMPED.\NSICILY. HERE WE COME.
Dialogue: 0.0:19:18.85.0:19:20.33.Default..0.0.0..I HOPE YOUR FAMILY LIKES ME.
Dialogue: 0.0:19:20.35.0:19:21.73.Default..0.0.0..OH. THEY WILL. BABY.
Dialogue: 0.0:19:21.76.0:19:23.27.Default..0.0.0..DON'T WORRY ABOUT IT.
Dialogue: 0.0:19:23.29.0:19:25.00.Default..0.0.0..YOU MIGHT BE MOVING\NTOO FAST FOR ME.
Dialogue: 0.0:19:25.03.0:19:27.61.Default..0.0.0..YEAH. BUDDY.
Dialogue: 0.0:19:27.63.0:19:29.97.Default..0.0.0..LOOK AT THESE MOUNTAINS.\NDUDE.
Dialogue: 0.0:19:30.00.0:19:31.14.Default..0.0.0..YEAH. IT'S CRAZY.
Dialogue: 0.0:19:31.17.0:19:33.48.Default..0.0.0..I'M SEEING SICILY\NFOR THE FIRST TIME.
Dialogue: 0.0:19:33.50.0:19:35.51.Default..0.0.0..IT LOOKS LIKE{\i1} JURASSIC PARK.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:19:35.54.0:19:37.88.Default..0.0.0..THERE'S VOLCANOES\NAND TREES AND MIST.
Dialogue: 0.0:19:37.91.0:19:39.78.Default..0.0.0..LIKE. KING KONG IS\NIN THE BUSHES.
Dialogue: 0.0:19:39.81.0:19:42.75.Default..0.0.0..AND IT'S REALLY NOTHING LIKE\NTHE ITALY WE'VE SEEN SO FAR.
Dialogue: 0.0:19:42.78.0:19:45.12.Default..0.0.0..YOU KNOW. GUYS. WE ARE DOING\NSOMETHING CRAZY RIGHT NOW.
Dialogue: 0.0:19:45.15.0:19:47.49.Default..0.0.0..I DON'T KNOW IF YOU REALIZE IT.\NBUT SICILY.
Dialogue: 0.0:19:47.51.0:19:49.63.Default..0.0.0..NO ONE VENTURES OUT THIS FAR.\NLIKE. FOR REAL.
Dialogue: 0.0:19:49.65.0:19:51.96.Default..0.0.0..THIS IS DEFINITELY\NSOME MAFIA-TYPE SHIT.
Dialogue: 0.0:19:51.99.0:19:53.76.Default..0.0.0..I DON'T KNOW IF YOU'VE EVER\NSEEN{\i1} GODFATHER II.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:19:53.79.0:19:58.04.Default..0.0.0..BUT FUCKIN'-\NIT'S IN SICILY.
Dialogue: 0.0:19:58.06.0:20:00.37.Default..0.0.0..WE PULL UP.\NAND THERE'S A RANCH.
Dialogue: 0.0:20:00.40.0:20:04.27.Default..0.0.0..I'M LIKE...\NFOUR GUIDOS IN THE WOODS?
Dialogue: 0.0:20:04.30.0:20:07.07.Default..0.0.0..EH... I DON'T KNOW ABOUT THAT.
Dialogue: 0.0:20:12.24.0:20:14.95.Default..0.0.0..RIGHT NOW.\NI AM IN THE MOTHERLAND.
Dialogue: 0.0:20:14.98.0:20:16.45.Default..0.0.0..MY MOTHER'S LAND. LITERALLY.
Dialogue: 0.0:20:16.48.0:20:19.92.Default..0.0.0..I'M ABOUT TO MEET MY FAMILY\NFOR THE FIRST TIME IN SICILY.
Dialogue: 0.0:20:19.95.0:20:22.29.Default..0.0.0..THIS IS WHERE I COME FROM.\NSO I'M EXCITED TO BE HERE.
Dialogue: 0.0:20:22.32.0:20:23.76.Default..0.0.0..HELLO.\N{\i1}CIAO.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:20:23.79.0:20:24.76.Default..0.0.0..HI.
Dialogue: 0.0:20:24.79.0:20:26.16.Default..0.0.0..MARIUCCA?\NYES.
Dialogue: 0.0:20:26.19.0:20:27.36.Default..0.0.0..{\i1}CIAO.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:20:27.39.0:20:29.87.Default..0.0.0..HI.\N{\i1}CIAO. CIAO.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:20:33.49.0:20:36.44.Default..0.0.0..THIS WAS LIKE\NTHE GUADAGNINO FAMILY TRAIN.
Dialogue: 0.0:20:36.46.0:20:38.74.Default..0.0.0..IT WAS JUST ONE\NFAMILY MEMBER AFTER ANOTHER
Dialogue: 0.0:20:38.77.0:20:41.15.Default..0.0.0..AFTER ANOTHER-\NWHOSE SON'S
Dialogue: 0.0:20:41.17.0:20:43.15.Default..0.0.0..UNCLE'S BROTHER'S\NNEPHEW'S
Dialogue: 0.0:20:43.17.0:20:45.12.Default..0.0.0..COUSIN'S BROTHER'S\NUNCLE'S SON.
Dialogue: 0.0:20:45.14.0:20:48.49.Default..0.0.0..I'M JUST LIKE...\N{\i1}CIAO?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:20:52.05.0:20:53.49.Default..0.0.0..EH. A LITTLE BIT.
Dialogue: 0.0:20:54.52.0:20:56.66.Default..0.0.0..THIS IS SICK.
Dialogue: 0.0:20:56.68.0:20:58.40.Default..0.0.0..THIS IS LIKE MAKEOUT POINT\NRIGHT HERE.
Dialogue: 0.0:20:58.42.0:21:00.43.Default..0.0.0..ALL RIGHT. LET'S GO.\NNO. I'M JUST KIDDING.
Dialogue: 0.0:21:02.42.0:21:05.10.Default..0.0.0..OH. MY GOD. WE HAVE TO TAKE\NA PICTURE OVER THERE.
Dialogue: 0.0:21:05.13.0:21:07.54.Default..0.0.0..THIS IS VERY ITALY.
Dialogue: 0.0:21:07.56.0:21:08.87.Default..0.0.0..WE SHOW UP\NAT OUR FIRST WINERY.
Dialogue: 0.0:21:08.90.0:21:10.71.Default..0.0.0..IT WAS VERY RUSTIC AND OLD
Dialogue: 0.0:21:10.73.0:21:12.98.Default..0.0.0..AND KIND OF HAD. LIKE.\NA CREEPY FEEL TO IT.
Dialogue: 0.0:21:13.00.0:21:14.64.Default..0.0.0..THIS IS ONE OF THE OLDEST\NCASTLES IN ITALY
Dialogue: 0.0:21:14.67.0:21:15.81.Default..0.0.0..STILL INHABITED.
Dialogue: 0.0:21:15.84.0:21:17.95.Default..0.0.0..WHAT WE DO TODAY WITH YOU\NIS WINE TASTING
Dialogue: 0.0:21:17.97.0:21:20.52.Default..0.0.0..AND TOURS OF THE 900-YEAR-OLD\NWINE CELLAR.
Dialogue: 0.0:21:20.54.0:21:21.75.Default..0.0.0..REALLY?\NIS THIS HAUNTED?
Dialogue: 0.0:21:21.78.0:21:24.45.Default..0.0.0..NOT ANYMORE.\NOH... NOT ANYMORE?
Dialogue: 0.0:21:24.48.0:21:25.82.Default..0.0.0..OKAY.\NFOLLOW ME.
Dialogue: 0.0:21:25.85.0:21:27.39.Default..0.0.0..EW. THIS IS CREEPY.
Dialogue: 0.0:21:27.42.0:21:29.16.Default..0.0.0..NO. I DON'T LIKE THIS.
Dialogue: 0.0:21:29.18.0:21:30.93.Default..0.0.0..DON'T GO OFF\NBY YOURSELF. STUPID.
Dialogue: 0.0:21:30.95.0:21:33.36.Default..0.0.0..SCREAM IF YOU GET LOST.
Dialogue: 0.0:21:33.39.0:21:35.23.Default..0.0.0..WE'RE WALKING\NDOWN IN THE CELLARS
Dialogue: 0.0:21:35.26.0:21:36.77.Default..0.0.0..AND THE BASEMENT\NAND STUFF LIKE THAT.
Dialogue: 0.0:21:36.79.0:21:38.27.Default..0.0.0..AND IT'S FRICKIN' SCARY!
Dialogue: 0.0:21:38.29.0:21:39.90.Default..0.0.0..LIKE. THIS IS HAUNTED.
Dialogue: 0.0:21:39.93.0:21:41.17.Default..0.0.0..BOO!
Dialogue: 0.0:21:43.13.0:21:44.84.Default..0.0.0..IT REALLY WAS HAUNTED.\NI COULD FEEL.
Dialogue: 0.0:21:44.87.0:21:46.24.Default..0.0.0..I GOT THE VIBE.
Dialogue: 0.0:21:46.27.0:21:48.01.Default..0.0.0..YOU WANT TO GO UPSTAIRS\NAND TASTE SOME WINE?
Dialogue: 0.0:21:48.04.0:21:50.18.Default..0.0.0..YEAH! WHOO-HOO!\NYEAH.
Dialogue: 0.0:21:50.20.0:21:51.68.Default..0.0.0..SHH.
Dialogue: 0.0:21:51.71.0:21:52.95.Default..0.0.0..I'LL BRING THIS\NBACK TO DEENA.
Dialogue: 0.0:21:56.98.0:21:58.19.Default..0.0.0..MICHAEL.
Dialogue: 0.0:21:58.21.0:21:59.19.Default..0.0.0..IF YOU WANT TO BE ITALIAN.
Dialogue: 0.0:21:59.21.0:22:00.59.Default..0.0.0..YOU HAVE TO KNOW\NHOW TO PLAY SOCCER.
Dialogue: 0.0:22:00.62.0:22:02.19.Default..0.0.0..I PLAY SOCCER.\NGOALKEEPER OVER HERE.
Dialogue: 0.0:22:02.22.0:22:03.99.Default..0.0.0..COME ON.
Dialogue: 0.0:22:05.95.0:22:07.43.Default..0.0.0..NICE SHOT!
Dialogue: 0.0:22:07.45.0:22:10.33.Default..0.0.0..All: OH!
Dialogue: 0.0:22:10.36.0:22:11.84.Default..0.0.0..NO. NO. NO.
Dialogue: 0.0:22:13.83.0:22:15.57.Default..0.0.0..NICE SHOT.\NTHAT WAS THE MONEY SHOT.
Dialogue: 0.0:22:15.60.0:22:16.91.Default..0.0.0..PERFECT.
Dialogue: 0.0:22:16.93.0:22:18.74.Default..0.0.0..LOOK. SHE'S GOT PICTURES\NOF MY FAMILY AT HOME.
Dialogue: 0.0:22:18.77.0:22:20.11.Default..0.0.0..OH. REALLY?\NYEAH. YEAH.
Dialogue: 0.0:22:20.13.0:22:21.61.Default..0.0.0..I WANT TO SHARE THIS ONE.
Dialogue: 0.0:22:21.64.0:22:23.85.Default..0.0.0..THERE'S ME WHEN I WAS\NLIKE FUCKING 13.
Dialogue: 0.0:22:23.87.0:22:26.45.Default..0.0.0..OH. LET ME SEE THAT.\NOH. NO WAY!
Dialogue: 0.0:22:26.47.0:22:28.55.Default..0.0.0..OH. WE GOTTA SEE THAT ONE.
Dialogue: 0.0:22:28.58.0:22:31.22.Default..0.0.0..All: AAH!
Dialogue: 0.0:22:31.25.0:22:32.39.Default..0.0.0..MY AWKWARD PHASE!
Dialogue: 0.0:22:32.41.0:22:34.29.Default..0.0.0..THAT WAS MY AWKWARD PHASE.
Dialogue: 0.0:22:34.32.0:22:35.29.Default..0.0.0..HEY. BABY.
Dialogue: 0.0:22:38.39.0:22:42.63.Default..0.0.0..THIS IS THE BEST DAY\NOF MY LIFE ON THE CAMERA.
Dialogue: 0.0:22:42.66.0:22:44.33.Default..0.0.0..WE'LL HAVE THE WINE TASTING\NWITH THE FOOD.
Dialogue: 0.0:22:44.36.0:22:45.67.Default..0.0.0..COOL.
Dialogue: 0.0:22:45.69.0:22:48.64.Default..0.0.0..THE FIRST ONE I'M GONNA\NSERVE IS THE SELVAPIANA.
Dialogue: 0.0:22:48.66.0:22:49.84.Default..0.0.0..THAT'S THE NAME\NOF THE WINERY.
Dialogue: 0.0:22:49.86.0:22:52.41.Default..0.0.0..OKAY. WE'RE GONNA START OFF\NWITH A 2009.
Dialogue: 0.0:22:52.43.0:22:53.71.Default..0.0.0..THIS IS THE VILLA WINE\NRIGHT NOW.
Dialogue: 0.0:22:53.73.0:22:55.38.Default..0.0.0..YOU CAN SEE THIS WALL IS-\NTHAT WAS. UH.
Dialogue: 0.0:22:55.40.0:22:56.95.Default..0.0.0..BOMBED DURING WORLD WAR II.
Dialogue: 0.0:22:56.97.0:22:58.98.Default..0.0.0..COOL. HISTORY. BOO!
Dialogue: 0.0:22:59.01.0:23:00.55.Default..0.0.0..LIKE. YOU KNOW?
Dialogue: 0.0:23:00.57.0:23:02.32.Default..0.0.0..LIKE. I'M NOT INTO GEOGRAPHY\NANYMORE.
Dialogue: 0.0:23:02.34.0:23:03.72.Default..0.0.0..GIVE ME FUCKIN' WINE.
Dialogue: 0.0:23:03.74.0:23:06.12.Default..0.0.0..THIS IS THE ULTIMATE WINE\NTO SERVE WITH A STEAK.
Dialogue: 0.0:23:06.15.0:23:07.12.Default..0.0.0..COLOR. WHAT THEY CALL...
Dialogue: 0.0:23:07.15.0:23:08.26.Default..0.0.0..EXCUSE ME.
Dialogue: 0.0:23:08.28.0:23:09.39.Default..0.0.0..WHEN YOU GRILL.
Dialogue: 0.0:23:09.42.0:23:10.93.Default..0.0.0..IT KIND OF MAKES IT\NA LITTLE BIT BITTER.
Dialogue: 0.0:23:10.95.0:23:12.03.Default..0.0.0..I JUST WANT HER TO SHUT UP
Dialogue: 0.0:23:12.05.0:23:13.46.Default..0.0.0..SO I CAN TALK ABOUT JIONNI\NRIGHT NOW.
Dialogue: 0.0:23:13.49.0:23:14.80.Default..0.0.0..LIKE. I'M GOING\NTHROUGH ISSUES.
Dialogue: 0.0:23:14.82.0:23:16.40.Default..0.0.0..I DON'T GIVE A FUCK\NABOUT HOW WINE'S MADE.
Dialogue: 0.0:23:16.42.0:23:17.50.Default..0.0.0..NOW JUST DO YOUR OWN THING.
Dialogue: 0.0:23:17.52.0:23:18.90.Default..0.0.0..LIKE YOU'RE JUST\NAT A REGULAR MEAL.
Dialogue: 0.0:23:18.93.0:23:20.44.Default..0.0.0..YOU DON'T WANT US\NTO DO OUR OWN THING.
Dialogue: 0.0:23:20.46.0:23:21.50.Default..0.0.0..WE'D EMBARRASS YOU.
Dialogue: 0.0:23:21.53.0:23:23.07.Default..0.0.0..ME AND DEENA WOULD BE\NON THE TABLES.
Dialogue: 0.0:23:23.10.0:23:24.84.Default..0.0.0..CAN WE TALK FOR A SECOND
Dialogue: 0.0:23:24.87.0:23:25.84.Default..0.0.0..AND MAKE ME HAPPY?
Dialogue: 0.0:23:25.87.0:23:26.84.Default..0.0.0..YEAH.
Dialogue: 0.0:23:26.87.0:23:28.31.Default..0.0.0..WHAT'S WRONG?\NJIONNI...
Dialogue: 0.0:23:28.34.0:23:29.65.Default..0.0.0..YEAH.\NWHAT AM I GONNA DO?
Dialogue: 0.0:23:29.67.0:23:31.75.Default..0.0.0..THAT THING WITH FREAKING VINNY\NCOULD HAVE RUINED IT.
Dialogue: 0.0:23:31.77.0:23:33.12.Default..0.0.0..YEAH. WHY'D YOU DO THAT?
Dialogue: 0.0:23:33.14.0:23:35.59.Default..0.0.0..'CAUSE HE PISSED ME OFF\NTO THE POINT WHERE...
Dialogue: 0.0:23:35.61.0:23:37.22.Default..0.0.0..AT THIS MOMENT.\NI KNOW YOU WANT SOMEONE.
Dialogue: 0.0:23:37.24.0:23:39.22.Default..0.0.0..BUT BY YOU DOING THAT\NWITH VINNY... NO OFFENSE...
Dialogue: 0.0:23:39.25.0:23:40.52.Default..0.0.0..LIKE. THE DAMAGE IS DONE.
Dialogue: 0.0:23:40.55.0:23:42.76.Default..0.0.0..I WANT TO. LIKE.\NPUT IT OUT THERE.
Dialogue: 0.0:23:42.78.0:23:44.23.Default..0.0.0..I WANT TO BE WITH HIM.\NTHOUGH.
Dialogue: 0.0:23:44.25.0:23:46.76.Default..0.0.0..HONESTLY. I REALLY THINK\NAT THIS POINT.
Dialogue: 0.0:23:46.79.0:23:47.86.Default..0.0.0..YOU SHOULD MOVE ON.
Dialogue: 0.0:23:47.89.0:23:49.40.Default..0.0.0..I DO TOO.
Dialogue: 0.0:23:49.42.0:23:50.73.Default..0.0.0..IF YOU WANT\NMY REAL OPINION.
Dialogue: 0.0:23:50.76.0:23:52.34.Default..0.0.0..THAT KID WON'T\NFORGIVE YOU FOR IT.
Dialogue: 0.0:23:52.36.0:23:55.51.Default..0.0.0..SO YOU GOTTA\NMAN UP TO YOUR MISTAKE
Dialogue: 0.0:23:55.53.0:23:57.24.Default..0.0.0..AND REALIZE THAT IT'S OVER\NBECAUSE OF THAT.
Dialogue: 0.0:23:57.26.0:23:59.04.Default..0.0.0..I LOVE HIM.\NNO. YOU DON'T.
Dialogue: 0.0:23:59.07.0:24:04.01.Default..0.0.0..IF YOU LOVED HIM. YOU WOULDN'T\NHAVE DONE THAT WITH VINNY.
Dialogue: 0.0:24:04.04.0:24:05.52.Default..0.0.0..JENNI JUST TOLD\NNICOLE THE TRUTH.
Dialogue: 0.0:24:05.54.0:24:08.02.Default..0.0.0..YOU KNOW WHEN SOMEBODY TELLS YOU\NYOU'RE DOING SOMETHING WRONG.
Dialogue: 0.0:24:08.04.0:24:09.42.Default..0.0.0..AND YOU DON'T WANNA.\NLIKE. HEAR IT?
Dialogue: 0.0:24:09.44.0:24:10.99.Default..0.0.0..THAT'S WHAT I FEEL LIKE\NNICOLE IS DOING.
Dialogue: 0.0:24:11.01.0:24:12.56.Default..0.0.0..HONESTLY. THOUGH.\NI'M CALLING YOU OUT
Dialogue: 0.0:24:12.58.0:24:13.72.Default..0.0.0..ON YOU BEING WRONG\NRIGHT NOW
Dialogue: 0.0:24:13.75.0:24:15.56.Default..0.0.0..FOR THE SIMPLE FACT THAT\NYOU LAID UP IN HIS BED...
Dialogue: 0.0:24:15.58.0:24:17.49.Default..0.0.0..I TOLD YOU WHY I DID THAT-\NTHE ONLY REASON WHY...
Dialogue: 0.0:24:17.52.0:24:19.16.Default..0.0.0..IT DOESN'T MATTER.\NTHAT IS NOT AN EXCUSE.
Dialogue: 0.0:24:19.19.0:24:20.63.Default..0.0.0..'CAUSE I WANTED TO BE\NDONE WITH HIM.
Dialogue: 0.0:24:20.65.0:24:23.57.Default..0.0.0..WELL. YOU ARE NOW.
Dialogue: 0.0:24:23.59.0:24:25.13.Default..0.0.0..YOU CAN'T CHANGE IT.\NTHE DAMAGE IS DONE.
Dialogue: 0.0:24:25.16.0:24:27.17.Default..0.0.0..SHE'S BEING THE WORST\NBEST FRIEND THIS WHOLE TIME.
Dialogue: 0.0:24:27.19.0:24:28.47.Default..0.0.0..THE WORST.
Dialogue: 0.0:24:28.50.0:24:30.01.Default..0.0.0..AND ON TOP OF\NWHAT MIKE'S SAYING...
Dialogue: 0.0:24:30.03.0:24:31.37.Default..0.0.0..SO THAT'S WHEN\NI WAS LIKE. "BYE."
Dialogue: 0.0:24:31.40.0:24:32.71.Default..0.0.0..THIS KID IS GOING\NTO HAVE ENOUGH.
Dialogue: 0.0:24:32.73.0:24:34.01.Default..0.0.0..I'M SORRY.
Dialogue: 0.0:24:34.03.0:24:36.41.Default..0.0.0..I WOULD NEVER DO THAT.\NI WOULD NEVER CHEAT ON HIM.
Dialogue: 0.0:24:36.44.0:24:37.78.Default..0.0.0..YOU DID. THOUGH.
Dialogue: 0.0:24:37.81.0:24:41.22.Default..0.0.0..THAT KID WILL HAVE ENOUGH.\NAND HE IS GONE.
Dialogue: 0.0:24:41.24.0:24:44.99.Default..0.0.0..SO ACCEPT IT AND MOVE ON.
Dialogue: 0.0:24:45.01.0:24:47.16.Default..0.0.0..YOU'RE FUCKING AIRING YOUR\NBEST FRIEND OUT RIGHT NOW.
Dialogue: 0.0:24:47.18.0:24:48.49.Default..0.0.0..WHAT THE FUCK?
Dialogue: 0.0:24:48.52.0:24:50.43.Default..0.0.0..DO YOU WANT MY OPINION.\NOR DO YOU WANT THE TRUTH?
Dialogue: 0.0:24:50.45.0:24:52.33.Default..0.0.0..JENNI'S BEING SUCH\NA BITCH TO ME.
Dialogue: 0.0:24:52.35.0:24:54.60.Default..0.0.0..I CAN'T EVEN TAKE HER.
Dialogue: 0.0:24:54.62.0:24:57.00.Default..0.0.0..I WANT TO KNOW RIGHT NOW\NWHAT YOU'VE DONE WITH VINNY.
Dialogue: 0.0:24:57.02.0:24:58.96.Default..0.0.0..HE {...} ME.\NAND THAT'S IT.
Dialogue: 0.0:25:09.44.0:25:12.32.Default..0.0.0..I WOULD NEVER DO THAT.\NI WOULD NEVER CHEAT ON HIM.
Dialogue: 0.0:25:12.34.0:25:13.85.Default..0.0.0..YOU DID. THOUGH.
Dialogue: 0.0:25:13.87.0:25:15.15.Default..0.0.0..I WANT TO BE WITH THIS KID.
Dialogue: 0.0:25:15.18.0:25:18.22.Default..0.0.0..HE IS NOT FOR YOU.\NMM-MM.
Dialogue: 0.0:25:18.25.0:25:20.32.Default..0.0.0..NICOLE STOPS THE WINE TASTING
Dialogue: 0.0:25:20.35.0:25:23.99.Default..0.0.0..AND WANTS OUR OPINION\NON HER AND JIONNI.
Dialogue: 0.0:25:24.02.0:25:26.23.Default..0.0.0..IF YOU LOVED HIM. YOU WOULDN'T\NHAVE DONE THAT WITH VINNY.
Dialogue: 0.0:25:26.25.0:25:27.36.Default..0.0.0..WE DIDN'T HAVE SEX. OKAY?
Dialogue: 0.0:25:27.39.0:25:28.70.Default..0.0.0..I MEAN. I WAS RIGHT THERE.
Dialogue: 0.0:25:28.72.0:25:30.47.Default..0.0.0..SO I'M THINKING IN MY HEAD.\NLIKE. SHE DID SEX.
Dialogue: 0.0:25:30.49.0:25:32.24.Default..0.0.0..BUT I'M NOT GONNA PUT HER\NON BLAST LIKE THAT.
Dialogue: 0.0:25:32.26.0:25:34.57.Default..0.0.0..AT THE TIME. HONESTLY. I WAS.\NLIKE. I DON'T GIVE A FUCK.
Dialogue: 0.0:25:34.60.0:25:36.07.Default..0.0.0..ME AND JIONNI ARE DONE.
Dialogue: 0.0:25:36.10.0:25:38.38.Default..0.0.0..I'M DONE WITH THIS KID.\NHE'S MAKING ME FEEL MISERABLE.
Dialogue: 0.0:25:38.40.0:25:40.58.Default..0.0.0..NOW... NOW THAT I THINK\NABOUT IT.
Dialogue: 0.0:25:40.60.0:25:43.75.Default..0.0.0..I FUCKING LOVE HIM.\NAND I CAN'T BELIEVE I DID THAT.
Dialogue: 0.0:25:43.77.0:25:45.28.Default..0.0.0..HE'S GONNA BE\NSO BEYOND HUMILIATED
Dialogue: 0.0:25:45.31.0:25:47.62.Default..0.0.0..FROM THE SIMPLE FACT THAT\NHIS GIRLFRIEND. AFTER TWO HOURS
Dialogue: 0.0:25:47.64.0:25:50.69.Default..0.0.0..OF GETTING IN A FIGHT.\NHOOKED UP WITH VINNY.
Dialogue: 0.0:25:50.71.0:25:52.96.Default..0.0.0..HE'LL NEVER ACCEPT IT.\NHE'LL NEVER GO ON THAT...
Dialogue: 0.0:25:52.98.0:25:55.26.Default..0.0.0..AND I DON'T WANT TO BE\NTHAT PERSON TO SAY IT TO YOU.
Dialogue: 0.0:25:55.28.0:25:58.18.Default..0.0.0..BUT AS A BEST FRIEND.\NMOVE ON.
Dialogue: 0.0:26:00.09.0:26:01.70.Default..0.0.0..MY BEST FRIEND\NWOULD NEVER DO THAT TO ME
Dialogue: 0.0:26:01.72.0:26:03.27.Default..0.0.0..AND JUST SAY SHIT.
Dialogue: 0.0:26:03.29.0:26:08.16.Default..0.0.0..AND JENNI'S REALLY NOT THERE\NFOR ME LIKE I THOUGHT SHE WAS.
Dialogue: 0.0:26:12.43.0:26:14.38.Default..0.0.0..GETTING TO KNOW MY FAMILY\NIS LIKE AN EXPERIENCE.
Dialogue: 0.0:26:14.40.0:26:16.15.Default..0.0.0..IT'S LIKE A CHOREOGRAPHY.\NIT'S LIKE A DANCE.
Dialogue: 0.0:26:20.07.0:26:21.48.Default..0.0.0..PAULY. IS THAT GOOD?
Dialogue: 0.0:26:21.51.0:26:24.19.Default..0.0.0..IT'S LIKE COURSE AFTER COURSE\NAFTER COURSE.
Dialogue: 0.0:26:24.21.0:26:26.16.Default..0.0.0..SO MUCH FOOD.\NJUST LIKE BACK HOME.
Dialogue: 0.0:26:26.18.0:26:29.13.Default..0.0.0..THEY LITERALLY KEEP\NPILING IT ON.
Dialogue: 0.0:26:29.15.0:26:31.59.Default..0.0.0..-{\i1} MANGIA. MANGIA!{\i0}\NMY STOMACH'S GONNA EXPLODE.
Dialogue: 0.0:26:31.62.0:26:34.30.Default..0.0.0..GUYS. LEAVE SOME ROOM\NBECAUSE IT'S NOT OVER YET.
Dialogue: 0.0:26:34.32.0:26:36.37.Default..0.0.0..WE JUST STARTED.
Dialogue: 0.0:26:38.66.0:26:41.14.Default..0.0.0..-{\i1} SALUD. SALUD.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:26:41.16.0:26:43.57.Default..0.0.0..MY FAMILY. THANK YOU
Dialogue: 0.0:26:43.60.0:26:45.64.Default..0.0.0..FOR LETTING ME AND MY FRIENDS\NCOME HERE.
Dialogue: 0.0:26:45.67.0:26:48.35.Default..0.0.0..MY WHOLE LIFE.\NI DREAMED ABOUT COMING HERE
Dialogue: 0.0:26:48.37.0:26:49.48.Default..0.0.0..AND HAVING THIS MEAL.
Dialogue: 0.0:26:49.50.0:26:52.42.Default..0.0.0..AND RIGHT NOW.\NIT'S COMING TRUE.
Dialogue: 0.0:26:52.44.0:26:54.59.Default..0.0.0..SO IT'S AMAZING. AND THANK YOU.\NAND I LOVE ALL OF YOU.
Dialogue: 0.0:26:54.61.0:26:55.82.Default..0.0.0..BEAUTIFUL.
Dialogue: 0.0:26:58.85.0:27:00.99.Default..0.0.0..YOU'RE WELCOME HERE\NANYTIME YOU WANT.
Dialogue: 0.0:27:01.02.0:27:02.68.Default..0.0.0..ALL RIGHT.\NTHANK YOU.
Dialogue: 0.0:27:11.09.0:27:12.07.Default..0.0.0..ARE YOU OKAY?
Dialogue: 0.0:27:12.09.0:27:13.30.Default..0.0.0..OH. NO.\NDID WE HURT HIS BIKE?
Dialogue: 0.0:27:13.33.0:27:14.64.Default..0.0.0..DID WE HURT HIS BIKE?
Dialogue: 0.0:27:14.66.0:27:16.47.Default..0.0.0..I WOULD SAY US GIRLS\NDEFINITELY WENT THROUGH
Dialogue: 0.0:27:16.50.0:27:17.91.Default..0.0.0..ABOUT. LIKE.\NTEN BOTTLES OF WINE.
Dialogue: 0.0:27:20.43.0:27:21.80.Default..0.0.0..-{\i1} ANDIAMO.{\i0}\NLET'S GO.
Dialogue: 0.0:27:23.94.0:27:25.88.Default..0.0.0..TODAY WAS A GOOD TIME.
Dialogue: 0.0:27:25.91.0:27:27.45.Default..0.0.0..IT'S NOT OVER YET.\NI'M HORNY.
Dialogue: 0.0:27:27.48.0:27:29.79.Default..0.0.0..IT SMELLS LIKE A FART.\NEWW. WHO JUST RIPPED ASS?
Dialogue: 0.0:27:29.81.0:27:31.01.Default..0.0.0..OH. MY GOD.
Dialogue: 0.0:27:34.05.0:27:36.16.Default..0.0.0..HERE YOU'LL FIND\NFOUR DIFFERENT TYPES OF WOOD.
Dialogue: 0.0:27:36.18.0:27:38.80.Default..0.0.0..AND SO THIS BLEND OF...
Dialogue: 0.0:27:38.82.0:27:40.56.Default..0.0.0..OH. MY GOD. I'M SO TIRED.
Dialogue: 0.0:27:40.59.0:27:42.10.Default..0.0.0..LIKE. I CAN'T EVEN\NDRINK WINE ANYMORE.
Dialogue: 0.0:27:42.12.0:27:44.03.Default..0.0.0..AND HE'S TALKING ABOUT\NWINE BARRELS
Dialogue: 0.0:27:44.06.0:27:46.34.Default..0.0.0..AND WAH. WAH. WAH.
Dialogue: 0.0:27:46.36.0:27:48.07.Default..0.0.0..AND DIFFERENT...
Dialogue: 0.0:27:48.10.0:27:51.71.Default..0.0.0..I THINK YOUR-\NYOUR FRIEND IS SLEEPING.
Dialogue: 0.0:27:51.73.0:27:54.38.Default..0.0.0..PROBABLY...
Dialogue: 0.0:27:54.40.0:27:56.88.Default..0.0.0..TOO MANY BOTTLES FOR...
Dialogue: 0.0:27:56.90.0:27:59.62.Default..0.0.0..I'M AWAKE.\NI'M AWAKE.
Dialogue: 0.0:27:59.64.0:28:01.32.Default..0.0.0..WE'RE SHOT.\NWE'RE DRUNK.
Dialogue: 0.0:28:01.34.0:28:03.92.Default..0.0.0..EVERYTHING THAT THIS GUY'S\NSAYING. WE ALREADY LEARNED.
Dialogue: 0.0:28:03.94.0:28:07.16.Default..0.0.0..SO IT'S JUST BASICALLY. LIKE.\NBRING ON THE WINE AND CHEESE.
Dialogue: 0.0:28:07.18.0:28:08.66.Default..0.0.0..WHAT KIND DID YOU GET?
Dialogue: 0.0:28:08.68.0:28:10.59.Default..0.0.0..I GUESS I'LL TAKE\NTHE STRONG ONE
Dialogue: 0.0:28:10.62.0:28:13.30.Default..0.0.0..THAT I ALWAYS FALL FOR.
Dialogue: 0.0:28:13.32.0:28:14.66.Default..0.0.0..MAYBE YOU SHOULDN'T.
Dialogue: 0.0:28:14.69.0:28:16.13.Default..0.0.0..ME?\NYEAH.
Dialogue: 0.0:28:16.16.0:28:17.43.Default..0.0.0..DON'T TALK SHIT.
Dialogue: 0.0:28:17.46.0:28:18.90.Default..0.0.0..'CAUSE I'LL AIR IT ALL OUT\NRIGHT NOW.
Dialogue: 0.0:28:18.93.0:28:21.10.Default..0.0.0..SNAP OUT OF IT.
Dialogue: 0.0:28:21.13.0:28:23.07.Default..0.0.0..I'M FINE.\NI'M ANNOYED.
Dialogue: 0.0:28:23.10.0:28:25.38.Default..0.0.0..DON'T BE MAD ABOUT\NTHE TRUTH.
Dialogue: 0.0:28:25.40.0:28:27.34.Default..0.0.0..THE WHOLE MIKE\NAND NICOLE DRAMA COMES UP.
Dialogue: 0.0:28:27.37.0:28:28.91.Default..0.0.0..I SEE. LIKE. MAYBE JENNI\NTHINKS. LIKE.
Dialogue: 0.0:28:28.94.0:28:30.35.Default..0.0.0..SOMETHING ELSE HAPPENED.
Dialogue: 0.0:28:30.37.0:28:33.22.Default..0.0.0..YOU ACT LIKE WE'RE NOT.\NLIKE. BEST FRIENDS.
Dialogue: 0.0:28:33.24.0:28:35.05.Default..0.0.0..WE ARE. BUT DON'T SIT HERE\NAND CRY
Dialogue: 0.0:28:35.08.0:28:36.32.Default..0.0.0..AND FEED PEOPLE LIES.
Dialogue: 0.0:28:36.34.0:28:37.95.Default..0.0.0..YOU'RE FEEDING EVERYBODY\NIN THIS HOUSE.
Dialogue: 0.0:28:37.98.0:28:39.66.Default..0.0.0..BESIDES ME. LIES.
Dialogue: 0.0:28:39.68.0:28:41.36.Default..0.0.0..MAYBE NICOLE\NISN'T BEING HONEST.
Dialogue: 0.0:28:41.38.0:28:43.36.Default..0.0.0..MAYBE MIKE'S TELLING THE TRUTH\NABOUT THEIR STORY.
Dialogue: 0.0:28:43.38.0:28:44.73.Default..0.0.0..IF I AM YOUR BEST FRIEND.
Dialogue: 0.0:28:44.75.0:28:46.63.Default..0.0.0..WHY CAN'T YOU HAVE SOMEONE\NTO TELL YOU THE TRUTH?
Dialogue: 0.0:28:46.65.0:28:48.06.Default..0.0.0..NO. ACTUALLY.\NYOU'RE NOT ANYMORE.
Dialogue: 0.0:28:48.09.0:28:50.60.Default..0.0.0..'CAUSE NONE OF MY BEST FRIENDS\NWOULD EVER SAY THAT.
Dialogue: 0.0:28:50.62.0:28:52.70.Default..0.0.0..I WOULD NEVER DO THAT\NTO A BEST FRIEND.
Dialogue: 0.0:28:52.73.0:28:54.27.Default..0.0.0..I'M NOT DOING ANYTHING.
Dialogue: 0.0:28:54.29.0:28:56.44.Default..0.0.0..YOU'RE FUCKING AIRING\NYOUR BEST FRIEND OUT RIGHT NOW.
Dialogue: 0.0:28:56.46.0:28:58.21.Default..0.0.0..WHAT THE FUCK\NARE YOU TALKING ABOUT?
Dialogue: 0.0:28:58.23.0:29:00.51.Default..0.0.0..YOU JUST SAID. "IF YOU'RE GONNA\NFUCKING AIR ME OUT..."
Dialogue: 0.0:29:00.53.0:29:01.71.Default..0.0.0..EXACTLY...
Dialogue: 0.0:29:01.74.0:29:03.18.Default..0.0.0..YOU'RE AIRING ME OUT\NRIGHT NOW.
Dialogue: 0.0:29:03.20.0:29:05.05.Default..0.0.0..WHY WOULD YOU MAKE\NA STUPID COMMENT LIKE THAT?
Dialogue: 0.0:29:05.07.0:29:06.58.Default..0.0.0..I DON'T NEED THIS.\NI NEED YOU.
Dialogue: 0.0:29:06.61.0:29:08.75.Default..0.0.0..I'M SUPPOSED TO SUGARCOAT IT?\NI AM HERE FOR YOU.
Dialogue: 0.0:29:08.78.0:29:11.66.Default..0.0.0..YEAH. YOU'RE SUPPOSED TO\NSUGARCOAT IT TO MAKE ME HAPPY.
Dialogue: 0.0:29:11.68.0:29:13.76.Default..0.0.0..NO. YOU... THAT'S WHY\NI ASKED YOU EARLIER.
Dialogue: 0.0:29:13.78.0:29:17.93.Default..0.0.0..DO YOU WANT MY OPINION.\NOR DO YOU WANT THE TRUTH?
Dialogue: 0.0:29:17.95.0:29:19.76.Default..0.0.0..JENNI'S BEING\NSUCH A BITCH TO ME.
Dialogue: 0.0:29:19.79.0:29:20.82.Default..0.0.0..I CAN'T EVEN TAKE HER.
Dialogue: 0.0:29:31.10.0:29:32.51.Default..0.0.0..YOU'RE GONNA HATE ME.
Dialogue: 0.0:29:32.53.0:29:33.84.Default..0.0.0..WHAT?
Dialogue: 0.0:29:33.87.0:29:35.95.Default..0.0.0..REMEMBER WHEN I TOLD YOU\NWHAT HAPPENED WITH VINNY?
Dialogue: 0.0:29:35.97.0:29:38.94.Default..0.0.0..YEAH.\NSOMETHING MORE HAPPENED.
Dialogue: 0.0:29:45.61.0:29:48.05.Default..0.0.0..I WOULD NEVER DO THAT\NTO A BEST FRIEND.
Dialogue: 0.0:29:49.75.0:29:52.13.Default..0.0.0..WOULD YOU SPEAK THE TRUTH.\NOR WOULD YOU SUGARCOAT IT?
Dialogue: 0.0:29:52.15.0:29:54.40.Default..0.0.0..WE WOULD FUCK... WE TELL EACH\NOTHER THE TRUTH ALL THE TIME.
Dialogue: 0.0:29:54.42.0:29:56.57.Default..0.0.0..THANK YOU. AND THAT'S EXACTLY\NWHAT I DID RIGHT HERE.
Dialogue: 0.0:29:56.59.0:29:58.24.Default..0.0.0..AND SHE\NCAN'T FUCKING HANDLE IT.
Dialogue: 0.0:29:58.26.0:30:02.21.Default..0.0.0..NICOLE. AT THIS POINT.\NIS MAKING UP LIES TO PEOPLE
Dialogue: 0.0:30:02.23.0:30:04.24.Default..0.0.0..SO THEY CAN SAY.\N"IT'S GONNA BE ALL RIGHT."
Dialogue: 0.0:30:04.26.0:30:06.61.Default..0.0.0..MAYBE IT'S NOT GONNA BE\NALL RIGHT. NICOLE.
Dialogue: 0.0:30:06.63.0:30:09.65.Default..0.0.0..AND YOU KNOW WHAT?\NMAN UP. AND FIX IT YOURSELF.
Dialogue: 0.0:30:09.67.0:30:11.75.Default..0.0.0..IF YOU WANT TO SHARE THIS TYPE\NOF INFORMATION WITH ME.
Dialogue: 0.0:30:11.77.0:30:13.48.Default..0.0.0..YOU HAVE TO EXPECT AN OPINION.
Dialogue: 0.0:30:13.51.0:30:15.75.Default..0.0.0..AND YOU GOT TO EXPECT WHEN\NYOU'RE GONNA DO WRONG OR RIGHT.
Dialogue: 0.0:30:15.78.0:30:16.95.Default..0.0.0..THAT'S NICOLE. THOUGH.
Dialogue: 0.0:30:16.98.0:30:18.99.Default..0.0.0..I FEEL LIKE JENNI...
Dialogue: 0.0:30:19.01.0:30:21.92.Default..0.0.0..LIKE. I LOVE HER TO DEATH.\NAND I WOULD FUCKING DIE FOR HER.
Dialogue: 0.0:30:21.95.0:30:23.36.Default..0.0.0..I SWEAR TO GOD.\NI WILL DIE FOR HER.
Dialogue: 0.0:30:23.38.0:30:27.40.Default..0.0.0..BUT SHE'S JUST BEING NOT\NA GOOD FRIEND TO ME.
Dialogue: 0.0:30:27.42.0:30:29.93.Default..0.0.0..THIS SHOULD BE\NA GREAT CAB RIDE.
Dialogue: 0.0:30:29.96.0:30:32.64.Default..0.0.0..YEAH.
Dialogue: 0.0:30:32.66.0:30:35.44.Default..0.0.0..OH. GOD.
Dialogue: 0.0:30:35.46.0:30:37.77.Default..0.0.0..HERE'S YOUR GLASSES.
Dialogue: 0.0:30:37.80.0:30:39.34.Default..0.0.0..OH. THANK YOU.\NI WAS LOOKING FOR THEM.
Dialogue: 0.0:30:39.37.0:30:40.54.Default..0.0.0..NICOLE.\NI'VE GOT A LITTLE BAG
Dialogue: 0.0:30:40.57.0:30:41.88.Default..0.0.0..FOR YOUR TO PUT\NALL THE STUFF IN.
Dialogue: 0.0:30:41.90.0:30:44.35.Default..0.0.0..THIS WHOLE TIME WAS SUPPOSED\NTO BE FUN. WINE NIGHT.
Dialogue: 0.0:30:44.37.0:30:47.62.Default..0.0.0..LIKE. AND THIS IS. LIKE.\NTHE WORST RIDE HOME.
Dialogue: 0.0:30:47.64.0:30:49.65.Default..0.0.0..LIKE. EVERYBODY'S QUIET.\NAND IT'S JUST AWKWARD.
Dialogue: 0.0:30:49.68.0:30:51.55.Default..0.0.0..AND I JUST WANT TO PUNCH\NSOMEBODY IN THE FACE.
Dialogue: 0.0:30:51.58.0:30:53.42.Default..0.0.0..LIKE. THIS IS NOT\NHOW IT WAS SUPPOSED TO BE.
Dialogue: 0.0:31:01.72.0:31:06.07.Default..0.0.0..♪ ♪
Dialogue: 0.0:31:06.09.0:31:08.41.Default..0.0.0..{\i1}SI.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:31:14.94.0:31:16.01.Default..0.0.0..EVERYBODY.
Dialogue: 0.0:31:16.04.0:31:18.11.Default..0.0.0..EVERY GENERATION IS TOGETHER\NRIGHT NOW.
Dialogue: 0.0:31:18.14.0:31:20.65.Default..0.0.0..EVEN THOUGH I NEVER MET\NTHESE PEOPLE IN MY LIFE.
Dialogue: 0.0:31:20.67.0:31:23.72.Default..0.0.0..WE'RE JUST BLOOD. SO IT'S JUST\NAN INSTANT CONNECTION.
Dialogue: 0.0:31:23.74.0:31:25.86.Default..0.0.0..THIS GUY RIGHT HERE-\NYOU SEE HOW MUCH HE'S SMILING?
Dialogue: 0.0:31:25.88.0:31:27.42.Default..0.0.0..HE MAKES US ALL SMILE.
Dialogue: 0.0:31:27.45.0:31:29.19.Default..0.0.0..AND THEIR FAMILY\NTAKES US IN LIKE FAMILY.
Dialogue: 0.0:31:29.22.0:31:30.63.Default..0.0.0..JUST LIKE\NTHE ONE BACK HOME. RIGHT?
Dialogue: 0.0:31:30.65.0:31:33.60.Default..0.0.0..WE LOVE YOUR FAMILY. KID.
Dialogue: 0.0:31:33.62.0:31:35.57.Default..0.0.0..I'M GLAD I DID THIS.
Dialogue: 0.0:31:35.59.0:31:38.03.Default..0.0.0..FOREVER-\NWE'LL REMEMBER THIS FOREVER.
Dialogue: 0.0:31:38.06.0:31:41.07.Default..0.0.0..YOU KNOW WHAT I MEAN?\NFOR REAL.
Dialogue: 0.0:31:41.10.0:31:42.81.Default..0.0.0..I WONDER WHAT THE GIRLS\NARE UP TO RIGHT NOW.
Dialogue: 0.0:31:48.74.0:31:51.05.Default..0.0.0..ME AND JENNI ARE NOT\NON GOOD TERMS RIGHT NOW.
Dialogue: 0.0:31:51.07.0:31:52.72.Default..0.0.0..IF YOU WANT TO KEEP\NYOUR FRIENDSHIP.
Dialogue: 0.0:31:52.74.0:31:54.08.Default..0.0.0..TALK TO HER ABOUT IT.
Dialogue: 0.0:31:54.11.0:31:57.82.Default..0.0.0..NICOLE KNOWS. AT THIS POINT.\NTHAT I AM AGITATED
Dialogue: 0.0:31:57.84.0:32:00.92.Default..0.0.0..WITH COVERING UP FOR HER.\NAND I AM DONE
Dialogue: 0.0:32:00.95.0:32:02.86.Default..0.0.0..TAKING ON HER ATTITUDE.
Dialogue: 0.0:32:02.88.0:32:03.93.Default..0.0.0..I'M OVER IT.
Dialogue: 0.0:32:03.95.0:32:04.99.Default..0.0.0..HEY. YOU.
Dialogue: 0.0:32:05.02.0:32:07.23.Default..0.0.0..NEVER AGAIN. BOO.
Dialogue: 0.0:32:07.25.0:32:10.07.Default..0.0.0..MM-MM.
Dialogue: 0.0:32:10.09.0:32:11.73.Default..0.0.0..OKAY.
Dialogue: 0.0:32:11.76.0:32:14.24.Default..0.0.0..I LOVE YOU.\NOKAY.
Dialogue: 0.0:32:14.26.0:32:16.41.Default..0.0.0..ME AND JENNI... LIKE.\NWHEN WE FIGHT. WE FIGHT.
Dialogue: 0.0:32:16.43.0:32:18.57.Default..0.0.0..AND WE WILL LEGIT KILL\NEACH OTHER.
Dialogue: 0.0:32:18.60.0:32:22.03.Default..0.0.0..BUT AT THE END OF THE DAY.\NWE STILL LOVE EACH OTHER.
Dialogue: 0.0:32:25.27.0:32:28.25.Default..0.0.0..I LOVE YOU SO MUCH.\NI LOVE YOU. TOO.
Dialogue: 0.0:32:28.28.0:32:30.25.Default..0.0.0..I'M SORRY.\NI HATED YOU SO MUCH.
Dialogue: 0.0:32:30.28.0:32:31.35.Default..0.0.0..I'M SORRY.
Dialogue: 0.0:32:31.38.0:32:33.52.Default..0.0.0..I DID TOO.
Dialogue: 0.0:32:33.55.0:32:35.53.Default..0.0.0..THE THING IS. I GET SO MAD.
Dialogue: 0.0:32:35.55.0:32:37.03.Default..0.0.0..'CAUSE I KNOW\NYOU JUST FEEL GUILTY.
Dialogue: 0.0:32:37.05.0:32:39.36.Default..0.0.0..BUT YOU'RE NOT DOING ANYTHING\NTO GET RID OF THE GUILT.
Dialogue: 0.0:32:39.39.0:32:40.86.Default..0.0.0..AND I'M...
Dialogue: 0.0:32:40.89.0:32:44.03.Default..0.0.0..YOU'RE FRUSTRATED\NWITH HOW I'M ACTING. I FEEL.
Dialogue: 0.0:32:44.06.0:32:45.32.Default..0.0.0..I GET IT.
Dialogue: 0.0:32:53.40.0:32:55.91.Default..0.0.0..OH. DAD. PLEASE ANSWER.\NI'M GONNA KILL YOU.
Dialogue: 0.0:32:55.94.0:32:58.68.Default..0.0.0..HELLO?
Dialogue: 0.0:32:58.71.0:33:00.15.Default..0.0.0..DAD?\NYES. DEAR?
Dialogue: 0.0:33:00.17.0:33:02.72.Default..0.0.0..I MISS JIONNI.
Dialogue: 0.0:33:02.74.0:33:05.55.Default..0.0.0..OKAY?
Dialogue: 0.0:33:05.58.0:33:07.56.Default..0.0.0..WHAT THE FUCK DO I DO?
Dialogue: 0.0:33:07.58.0:33:09.06.Default..0.0.0..WELL. I CAN TELL YOU THIS.
Dialogue: 0.0:33:09.08.0:33:12.23.Default..0.0.0..HE DID CHANGE\NHIS FACEBOOK TO SINGLE.
Dialogue: 0.0:33:12.25.0:33:14.23.Default..0.0.0..HE DID?
Dialogue: 0.0:33:14.25.0:33:16.23.Default..0.0.0..YEP.
Dialogue: 0.0:33:16.26.0:33:18.40.Default..0.0.0..BECAUSE THAT'S WHAT YOU SAID\NYOU WANTED DONE.
Dialogue: 0.0:33:18.43.0:33:22.04.Default..0.0.0..OH. MY GOD!
Dialogue: 0.0:33:22.06.0:33:24.67.Default..0.0.0..HE CHANGED HIS FACEBOOK STATUS\NTO SINGLE.
Dialogue: 0.0:33:24.70.0:33:26.11.Default..0.0.0..REALLY?
Dialogue: 0.0:33:26.13.0:33:27.58.Default..0.0.0..YEAH. THAT MEANS\NIT'S OFFICIAL.
Dialogue: 0.0:33:27.60.0:33:29.08.Default..0.0.0..HE'S AN IDIOT. BRO.
Dialogue: 0.0:33:29.10.0:33:32.35.Default..0.0.0..I FUCKIN' FUCKED UP.
Dialogue: 0.0:33:32.37.0:33:34.28.Default..0.0.0..OH. I HATE MYSELF.
Dialogue: 0.0:33:34.31.0:33:35.69.Default..0.0.0..YOU DIDN'T CAUSE THIS.
Dialogue: 0.0:33:35.71.0:33:37.02.Default..0.0.0..HE CAUSED THIS.
Dialogue: 0.0:33:37.04.0:33:38.52.Default..0.0.0..OKAY?
Dialogue: 0.0:33:38.55.0:33:39.86.Default..0.0.0..FINE.
Dialogue: 0.0:33:39.88.0:33:41.19.Default..0.0.0..I WILL CALL YOU\NIN A LITTLE BIT.
Dialogue: 0.0:33:41.21.0:33:44.03.Default..0.0.0..I LOVE YOU.\NI LOVE YOU TOO.
Dialogue: 0.0:33:44.05.0:33:45.36.Default..0.0.0..BYE.\NBYE.
Dialogue: 0.0:33:45.39.0:33:47.70.Default..0.0.0..SO. YOU KNOW. I JUST WANTED\NTO TALK TO JIONNI
Dialogue: 0.0:33:47.72.0:33:50.70.Default..0.0.0..AND JUST SAY. "FIRST OF ALL.\NI'M FUCKING PISSED AT YOU
Dialogue: 0.0:33:50.72.0:33:52.80.Default..0.0.0.."FOR CHANGING\NYOUR FACEBOOK STATUS TO SINGLE.
Dialogue: 0.0:33:52.83.0:33:55.20.Default..0.0.0.."LIKE. WHO DOES THAT. IF YOU\NREALLY WANT TO BE WITH ME?
Dialogue: 0.0:33:55.23.0:33:59.01.Default..0.0.0..AND ALSO. I HAVE TO TELL YOU\NSOMETHING REALLY BAD."
Dialogue: 0.0:34:02.40.0:34:04.55.Default..0.0.0..HELLO?
Dialogue: 0.0:34:04.57.0:34:05.58.Default..0.0.0..HI.
Dialogue: 0.0:34:05.61.0:34:07.72.Default..0.0.0..CAN I TALK TO YOU?
Dialogue: 0.0:34:07.74.0:34:09.49.Default..0.0.0..NO!\NWHY DO YOU WANT TO TALK TO ME?
Dialogue: 0.0:34:09.51.0:34:11.65.Default..0.0.0..YOU BROKE UP WITH ME!\NYOU BROKE MY FUCKING HEART!
Dialogue: 0.0:34:11.68.0:34:13.22.Default..0.0.0..I SAID. "A BREAK"!
Dialogue: 0.0:34:13.25.0:34:15.53.Default..0.0.0..I DIDN'T SAY I FUCKIN' WANT\NTO BREAK UP WITH YOU!
Dialogue: 0.0:34:15.55.0:34:16.96.Default..0.0.0..AND THEN MY DAD\NHAS TO FUCKING TELL ME
Dialogue: 0.0:34:16.98.0:34:18.63.Default..0.0.0..THAT YOU PUT ON FACEBOOK\NYOU'RE SINGLE?
Dialogue: 0.0:34:18.65.0:34:21.00.Default..0.0.0..ARE YOU THAT EXCITED\NTO GET FUCKING {...}?
Dialogue: 0.0:34:21.02.0:34:22.00.Default..0.0.0..REALLY?
Dialogue: 0.0:34:22.02.0:34:23.57.Default..0.0.0..WHY WOULD YOU DO THAT?
Dialogue: 0.0:34:23.59.0:34:25.13.Default..0.0.0..YESTERDAY\NON THE PHONE YOU SAID TO ME.
Dialogue: 0.0:34:25.16.0:34:26.54.Default..0.0.0.."I CAN'T BE WITH YOU ANYMORE.
Dialogue: 0.0:34:26.56.0:34:29.24.Default..0.0.0.."YOU TREAT ME LIKE SHIT.\NYOU MAKE ME A DIFFERENT PERSON."
Dialogue: 0.0:34:29.26.0:34:31.84.Default..0.0.0..YOU... WHY DO YOU THINK I SAID\NI WANTED A BREAK WITH YOU?
Dialogue: 0.0:34:31.87.0:34:35.01.Default..0.0.0..BECAUSE. OBVIOUSLY. YOU FUCKING\NSAID SOMETHING FUCKED UP TO ME.
Dialogue: 0.0:34:35.04.0:34:37.18.Default..0.0.0..DO YOU UNDERSTAND I LOVE YOU?\NWHAT?
Dialogue: 0.0:34:37.20.0:34:39.68.Default..0.0.0..I FUCKING LOVE YOU.\NAND I'M HURTING WITHOUT YOU.
Dialogue: 0.0:34:39.71.0:34:41.68.Default..0.0.0..ALL I DO... I WAKE UP.\NI GO TO SLEEP.
Dialogue: 0.0:34:41.71.0:34:42.85.Default..0.0.0..AND I THINK ABOUT YOU.
Dialogue: 0.0:34:42.88.0:34:44.49.Default..0.0.0..WHAT THE FUCK\NAM I GONNA DO?
Dialogue: 0.0:34:44.51.0:34:47.19.Default..0.0.0..WHAT. DO YOU THINK\NI DON'T THINK ABOUT YOU?
Dialogue: 0.0:34:47.21.0:34:48.86.Default..0.0.0..HONESTLY.\NI HAVE TO TELL YOU SOMETHING.
Dialogue: 0.0:34:48.88.0:34:51.53.Default..0.0.0..AND YOU'RE NEVER GONNA TALK\NTO ME AGAIN.
Dialogue: 0.0:34:51.55.0:34:53.03.Default..0.0.0..WHAT?\NWHAT'D YOU DO?
Dialogue: 0.0:34:53.05.0:34:55.67.Default..0.0.0..PLEASE DON'T HANG UP\NWHEN I TELL YOU THIS.
Dialogue: 0.0:34:55.69.0:34:58.73.Default..0.0.0..WHAT DID YOU DO?
Dialogue: 0.0:34:58.76.0:35:01.24.Default..0.0.0..AFTER WE GOT OFF THE PHONE.
Dialogue: 0.0:35:01.26.0:35:03.37.Default..0.0.0..I ENDED UP IN VINNY'S BED.
Dialogue: 0.0:35:03.40.0:35:05.21.Default..0.0.0..WE DIDN'T HAVE SEX.\NPLEASE DON'T HANG UP.
Dialogue: 0.0:35:05.23.0:35:07.38.Default..0.0.0..PLEASE DON'T HANG UP.
Dialogue: 0.0:35:07.40.0:35:09.21.Default..0.0.0..OH. PLEASE DON'T HANG UP.\NWE DIDN'T HAVE SEX.
Dialogue: 0.0:35:09.24.0:35:10.75.Default..0.0.0..PLEASE...
Dialogue: 0.0:35:10.77.0:35:12.18.Default..0.0.0..YOU HAD SEX.\NOR YOU DIDN'T HAVE SEX?
Dialogue: 0.0:35:12.21.0:35:13.55.Default..0.0.0..WE DIDN'T HAVE SEX.
Dialogue: 0.0:35:13.57.0:35:15.72.Default..0.0.0..PLEASE DON'T HANG UP.\NWE DIDN'T HAVE SEX.
Dialogue: 0.0:35:15.74.0:35:18.02.Default..0.0.0..DID YOU HOOK UP WITH HIM?\NYES.
Dialogue: 0.0:35:18.04.0:35:20.39.Default..0.0.0..ALL RIGHT. I'LL SEE YOU LATER.\NNO. PLEASE DON'T HANG UP.
Dialogue: 0.0:35:20.41.0:35:22.26.Default..0.0.0..PLEASE!\NPLEASE DON'T DO THIS TO ME.
Dialogue: 0.0:35:22.28.0:35:23.56.Default..0.0.0..NAH. WE'RE DONE.
Dialogue: 0.0:35:23.58.0:35:25.06.Default..0.0.0..NO!\NNO. NICOLE!
Dialogue: 0.0:35:25.08.0:35:26.73.Default..0.0.0..TELL VINNY. WHEN I SEE HIM.\NHE'S DEAD.
Dialogue: 0.0:35:26.75.0:35:28.06.Default..0.0.0..HE'S DONE!
Dialogue: 0.0:35:28.09.0:35:30.07.Default..0.0.0..PLEASE. JIONNI.\NPLEASE DON'T DO THIS TO ME!
Dialogue: 0.0:35:30.09.0:35:34.29.Default..0.0.0..PLEASE!
Dialogue: 0.0:35:51.28.0:35:59.28.Default..0.0.0..♪ ♪
Dialogue: 0.0:36:00.75.0:36:03.77.Default..0.0.0..STOP. DICK.
Dialogue: 0.0:36:03.79.0:36:06.17.Default..0.0.0..IT'S TIME TO GO.\NTHIS TRIP HAS COME TO AN END.
Dialogue: 0.0:36:06.19.0:36:07.77.Default..0.0.0..WE NEED TO HEAD BACK\NTO FIRENZE.
Dialogue: 0.0:36:07.79.0:36:09.14.Default..0.0.0..OKAY. BUDDY.\NTHANK YOU.
Dialogue: 0.0:36:09.16.0:36:10.84.Default..0.0.0..I CAN'T THANK YOU ENOUGH.\NTHANK YOU.
Dialogue: 0.0:36:10.86.0:36:13.54.Default..0.0.0..I WILL REMEMBER THE SICILY TRIP\NFOR THE REST OF MY LIFE.
Dialogue: 0.0:36:13.57.0:36:16.21.Default..0.0.0..I BROUGHT MY FAMILY\NWITH ME FROM JERSEY.
Dialogue: 0.0:36:16.24.0:36:19.68.Default..0.0.0..AND I CAME TO SICILY.\NTRACED MY ROOTS BACK.
Dialogue: 0.0:36:19.71.0:36:20.98.Default..0.0.0..AND I WILL RETURN.
Dialogue: 0.0:36:24.01.0:36:31.95.Default..0.0.0..♪ ♪
Dialogue: 0.0:36:36.76.0:36:37.73.Default..0.0.0..HELLO?
Dialogue: 0.0:36:37.76.0:36:38.90.Default..0.0.0..I JUST WANTED TO CALL YOU.
Dialogue: 0.0:36:38.93.0:36:40.94.Default..0.0.0..'CAUSE YOU'RE ON MY MIND\N24/7.
Dialogue: 0.0:36:40.96.0:36:43.01.Default..0.0.0..FIRST OFF.\NI WANNA KNOW RIGHT NOW.
Dialogue: 0.0:36:43.03.0:36:45.57.Default..0.0.0..WHAT DID YOU DO\NWITH VINNY?
Dialogue: 0.0:36:45.60.0:36:46.88.Default..0.0.0..BABE. COME ON.
Dialogue: 0.0:36:46.90.0:36:49.48.Default..0.0.0..ME AND VINNY.\NI FEEL. TRIED TO HAVE SEX.
Dialogue: 0.0:36:49.50.0:36:50.51.Default..0.0.0..BUT IT JUST\NDIDN'T WORK.
Dialogue: 0.0:36:50.54.0:36:52.25.Default..0.0.0..BUT I DON'T REMEMBER.
Dialogue: 0.0:36:52.27.0:36:54.68.Default..0.0.0..I WANNA KNOW RIGHT NOW\NWHAT YOU'VE DONE WITH VINNY.
Dialogue: 0.0:36:54.71.0:36:57.72.Default..0.0.0..HE {...} ME.\NAND THAT'S IT.
Dialogue: 0.0:36:57.74.0:37:00.36.Default..0.0.0..WE BREAK UP AND YOU GO\NFUCK AROUND WITH VINNY
Dialogue: 0.0:37:00.38.0:37:01.42.Default..0.0.0..AN HOUR LATER?
Dialogue: 0.0:37:01.45.0:37:04.23.Default..0.0.0..I FUCKED UP.\NI FUCKED UP.
Dialogue: 0.0:37:04.25.0:37:06.56.Default..0.0.0..NICOLE. I'VE NEVER BEEN\NFUCKING CRUSHED
Dialogue: 0.0:37:06.59.0:37:07.80.Default..0.0.0..THIS BAD IN MY LIFE.
Dialogue: 0.0:37:07.82.0:37:09.73.Default..0.0.0..YOU DON'T GIVE A SHIT\NABOUT ME. NICOLE.
Dialogue: 0.0:37:09.76.0:37:11.90.Default..0.0.0..OH. YOU'RE SUCH\NA FUCKING LIE.
Dialogue: 0.0:37:11.93.0:37:13.57.Default..0.0.0..YOU'RE ALL\NI THINK ABOUT.
Dialogue: 0.0:37:13.59.0:37:14.90.Default..0.0.0..I'M A FUCKING IDIOT.
Dialogue: 0.0:37:14.93.0:37:17.94.Default..0.0.0..I'M SO FUCKING STUPID\NFOR DOING THAT TO YOU.
Dialogue: 0.0:37:17.97.0:37:19.28.Default..0.0.0..I GET I FUCKED UP!
Dialogue: 0.0:37:19.30.0:37:21.14.Default..0.0.0..I'M SORRY!
Dialogue: 0.0:37:21.17.0:37:23.85.Default..0.0.0..BABE. I'M SORRY.\NNICOLE. I...
Dialogue: 0.0:37:23.87.0:37:25.65.Default..0.0.0..LISTEN. DO YOU\NWANNA BE TOGETHER?
Dialogue: 0.0:37:25.67.0:37:27.95.Default..0.0.0..YES! OR I WOULDN'T BE\NTALKING TO YOU RIGHT NOW.
Dialogue: 0.0:37:27.97.0:37:31.39.Default..0.0.0..ARE YOU KIDDING?\NRIGHT.
Dialogue: 0.0:37:31.41.0:37:34.06.Default..0.0.0..I'LL GIVE YOU\NANOTHER CHANCE.
Dialogue: 0.0:37:34.08.0:37:37.03.Default..0.0.0..THANK YOU.
Dialogue: 0.0:37:37.05.0:37:39.26.Default..0.0.0..JUST DON'T FUCK ME OVER.
Dialogue: 0.0:37:39.29.0:37:41.90.Default..0.0.0..I WON'T FUCK YOU OVER.\NI PROMISE.
Dialogue: 0.0:37:41.92.0:37:44.17.Default..0.0.0..ALL RIGHT.\NI GOTTA GO. OKAY?
Dialogue: 0.0:37:44.19.0:37:45.60.Default..0.0.0..OKAY. BYE.
Dialogue: 0.0:37:45.63.0:37:49.41.Default..0.0.0..BYE.
Dialogue: 0.0:37:50.60.0:37:51.87.Default..0.0.0..SORRY!
Dialogue: 0.0:37:51.90.0:37:55.31.Default..0.0.0..I'M SO HAPPY THAT\NME AND JIONNI ARE TOGETHER.
Dialogue: 0.0:37:55.34.0:37:56.75.Default..0.0.0..FEEL GOOD?
Dialogue: 0.0:37:56.77.0:37:58.58.Default..0.0.0..OH. MY GOD. HE'S GIVING ME\NA SECOND CHANCE.
Dialogue: 0.0:37:58.60.0:38:01.62.Default..0.0.0..AWW. THANK FUCKING\NJESUS CHRIST.
Dialogue: 0.0:38:01.64.0:38:04.12.Default..0.0.0..AND I'M SO HAPPY THAT HE'S\NGIVING ME A SECOND CHANCE.
Dialogue: 0.0:38:04.14.0:38:05.52.Default..0.0.0..LIKE. I LOVE HIM.
Dialogue: 0.0:38:05.55.0:38:06.52.Default..0.0.0..I'M IN LOVE!
Dialogue: 0.0:38:06.55.0:38:08.29.Default..0.0.0..LIKE. WHAT THE FUCK?
Dialogue: 0.0:38:08.31.0:38:11.06.Default..0.0.0..I'M IN LOVE.
Dialogue: 0.0:38:11.08.0:38:12.06.Default..0.0.0..HM!
Dialogue: 0.0:38:12.09.0:38:13.20.Default..0.0.0..SEE?
Dialogue: 0.0:38:13.22.0:38:14.20.Default..0.0.0..OOH!
Dialogue: 0.0:38:14.22.0:38:15.63.Default..0.0.0..OH. MY GOD.\NI CAN'T WAIT
Dialogue: 0.0:38:15.66.0:38:17.47.Default..0.0.0..TO GO RUN AND HUG\NAND KISS SAM.
Dialogue: 0.0:38:17.49.0:38:20.40.Default..0.0.0..SHUT THE FUCK UP.
Dialogue: 0.0:38:20.43.0:38:22.11.Default..0.0.0..YO.\NHI. GIRLS.
Dialogue: 0.0:38:22.13.0:38:24.81.Default..0.0.0..HEY!
Dialogue: 0.0:38:24.83.0:38:28.14.Default..0.0.0..MM. I MISSED YOU SO MUCH.\NYEAH?
Dialogue: 0.0:38:28.17.0:38:29.81.Default..0.0.0..CAN WE TALK\NABOUT THE OTHER NIGHT?
Dialogue: 0.0:38:29.84.0:38:31.28.Default..0.0.0..SO I KNOW WHAT\NTO TELL JIONNI?
Dialogue: 0.0:38:31.30.0:38:32.75.Default..0.0.0..WHAT DO YOU MEAN.\NWHAT HAPPENED?
Dialogue: 0.0:38:32.77.0:38:34.08.Default..0.0.0..I ASKED YOU\NIF YOU WERE DRUNK.
Dialogue: 0.0:38:34.11.0:38:35.32.Default..0.0.0..YOU SAID NO.
Dialogue: 0.0:38:35.34.0:38:37.09.Default..0.0.0..I WANNA KNOW WHAT HAPPENED\NWITH ME AND VINNY
Dialogue: 0.0:38:37.11.0:38:38.25.Default..0.0.0..'CAUSE I DON'T\NEXACTLY KNOW.
Dialogue: 0.0:38:38.28.0:38:39.49.Default..0.0.0..LIKE. DID WE\NHAVE SEX AND STUFF?
Dialogue: 0.0:38:39.51.0:38:40.76.Default..0.0.0..LIKE. I HAVE NO IDEA.
Dialogue: 0.0:38:40.78.0:38:42.69.Default..0.0.0..YOU CAN'T\NREMEMBER WHAT YOU DID?
Dialogue: 0.0:38:42.72.0:38:44.23.Default..0.0.0..THAT'S HOW DRUNK YOU WERE?
Dialogue: 0.0:38:44.25.0:38:45.93.Default..0.0.0..I DON'T BELIEVE YOU.
Dialogue: 0.0:38:45.95.0:38:48.77.Default..0.0.0..I REMEMBER CERTAIN THINGS\NTHAT I DON'T WANNA SAY.
Dialogue: 0.0:38:48.79.0:38:52.00.Default..0.0.0..DID WE {...} SMUSH?
Dialogue: 0.0:38:52.03.0:38:53.14.Default..0.0.0..DON'T SAY {...}.
Dialogue: 0.0:38:53.16.0:38:54.54.Default..0.0.0..I JUST WANNA KNOW\NWHAT TO TELL HIM.
Dialogue: 0.0:38:54.56.0:38:56.00.Default..0.0.0..YOU WANNA KNOW\NEVERY LITTLE DETAIL?
Dialogue: 0.0:38:56.03.0:38:57.14.Default..0.0.0..MM-HMM.
Dialogue: 0.0:38:57.16.0:38:58.61.Default..0.0.0..ALL RIGHT.\NLET'S GO OUTSIDE.
Dialogue: 0.0:38:58.63.0:39:00.18.Default..0.0.0..IT WAS LIKE\NA GLITCH IN THE MATRIX.
Dialogue: 0.0:39:00.20.0:39:02.55.Default..0.0.0..LIKE. EVERYTHING IS HAPPENING\NTHE WAY IT'S SUPPOSED TO BE.
Dialogue: 0.0:39:02.57.0:39:04.21.Default..0.0.0..THEN ALL OF A SUDDEN.\NGLITCH IN THE MATRIX.
Dialogue: 0.0:39:04.24.0:39:05.35.Default..0.0.0..WHOA. BANG SNOOKI.
Dialogue: 0.0:39:05.37.0:39:07.18.Default..0.0.0..AND THEN EVERYTHING\NJUST CONTINUED
Dialogue: 0.0:39:07.21.0:39:08.65.Default..0.0.0..THE WAY IT WAS\NHAPPENING BEFORE.
Dialogue: 0.0:39:08.68.0:39:09.69.Default..0.0.0..SO YOU WERE\NIN MY BED.
Dialogue: 0.0:39:09.71.0:39:11.09.Default..0.0.0..YOU CLIMBED INTO MY BED.\NMM-HMM.
Dialogue: 0.0:39:11.11.0:39:13.19.Default..0.0.0..AND THEN...
Dialogue: 0.0:39:13.21.0:39:14.62.Default..0.0.0..WHATEVER.\NWE WERE JUST CUDDLING.
Dialogue: 0.0:39:14.65.0:39:16.53.Default..0.0.0..AND THEN. LIKE.\NYOU STARTED. LIKE.
Dialogue: 0.0:39:16.55.0:39:17.79.Default..0.0.0..KISSING MY NECK\NA LITTLE BIT.
Dialogue: 0.0:39:17.82.0:39:19.73.Default..0.0.0..AND THEN YOU JUST KEPT SAYING.\NLIKE. "{...} ME."
Dialogue: 0.0:39:21.15.0:39:22.33.Default..0.0.0..STOP. STOP.
Dialogue: 0.0:39:22.36.0:39:23.87.Default..0.0.0..YOU WERE. LIKE. "FUCK ME.\NI'M HORNY."
Dialogue: 0.0:39:23.89.0:39:25.10.Default..0.0.0..STOP IT!\N{...}.
Dialogue: 0.0:39:25.13.0:39:26.50.Default..0.0.0..VINNY. YOU DON'T\NHAVE TO SAY THAT!
Dialogue: 0.0:39:26.53.0:39:28.30.Default..0.0.0..OH. MY GOD!\NWHY WOULD YOU SAY THAT?
Dialogue: 0.0:39:29.66.0:39:30.74.Default..0.0.0..OH. MY GOD.
Dialogue: 0.0:39:30.76.0:39:32.01.Default..0.0.0..WHATEVER.
Dialogue: 0.0:39:32.03.0:39:35.91.Default..0.0.0..I THOUGHT WE WERE\NJUST. LIKE. CUDDLING AND...
Dialogue: 0.0:39:35.94.0:39:38.65.Default..0.0.0..MY {...} WAS CUDDLING\NWITH YOUR {...}. BUT...
Dialogue: 0.0:39:38.67.0:39:42.15.Default..0.0.0..I HAVE TO TELL HIM.
Dialogue: 0.0:39:42.18.0:39:45.39.Default..0.0.0..TELL HIM.\NDON'T LIE.
Dialogue: 0.0:39:45.41.0:39:47.92.Default..0.0.0..I REALLY. HONESTLY\NTHOUGHT WE DIDN'T HAVE SEX.
Dialogue: 0.0:39:47.95.0:39:49.26.Default..0.0.0..LIKE. I BLACKED OUT\NA LITTLE BIT.
Dialogue: 0.0:39:49.28.0:39:50.89.Default..0.0.0..WHAT ARE YOU GONNA DO?
Dialogue: 0.0:39:50.92.0:39:52.10.Default..0.0.0..FREAKING OUT.
Dialogue: 0.0:39:52.12.0:39:53.36.Default..0.0.0..JUST GO SOMEWHERE.
Dialogue: 0.0:39:53.39.0:39:56.67.Default..0.0.0..AND I TOLD JIONNI\NTHAT WE JUST {...} POPPED.
Dialogue: 0.0:39:56.69.0:39:58.30.Default..0.0.0..NOW I HAVE TO CALL HIM BACK\NAND SAY.
Dialogue: 0.0:39:58.33.0:40:00.30.Default..0.0.0.."WELL. YOU SITTIN' DOWN?
Dialogue: 0.0:40:00.33.0:40:03.44.Default..0.0.0..WE ACTUALLY REALLY HAD SEX."
Dialogue: 0.0:40:03.46.0:40:05.07.Default..0.0.0..OH. DEAR SHIT BALLS.
Dialogue: 0.0:40:05.10.0:40:07.38.Default..0.0.0..OH!
Dialogue: 0.0:40:10.37.0:40:12.82.Default..0.0.0..HELLO?\NYOU'RE GONNA HATE ME.
Dialogue: 0.0:40:12.84.0:40:14.15.Default..0.0.0..WHAT?
Dialogue: 0.0:40:14.17.0:40:17.52.Default..0.0.0..REMEMBER WHAT I TOLD YOU\NWHAT HAPPENED WITH VINNY?
Dialogue: 0.0:40:17.54.0:40:20.76.Default..0.0.0..YEAH.\NSOMETHING MORE HAPPENED.
Dialogue: 0.0:40:20.78.0:40:22.39.Default..0.0.0..WHAT?
Dialogue: 0.0:40:22.42.0:40:24.59.Default..0.0.0..UH...
Dialogue: 0.0:40:24.62.0:40:27.43.Default..0.0.0..I DON'T EVEN\NWANNA SAY IT.
Dialogue: 0.0:40:27.45.0:40:28.97.Default..0.0.0..SAY WHAT?
Dialogue: 0.0:40:28.99.0:40:30.63.Default..0.0.0..UH...
Dialogue: 0.0:40:30.66.0:40:33.46.Default..0.0.0..WE HAD SEX.
